(4, 24, 1, 3578, 35, 'full-stack-developer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/full-stack-developer-3333630?fr=21&searchRequestToken=40632c37-86df-423b-fba5-41dfc7c017a7&sectionRank=1', 'FULL STACK DEVELOPER', 'Surabaya', '<p><b>General Main Job Description </b>:</p><p>\r\nHighly skilled computer programmer who is proficient in both front, back end coding. Primary\r\nresponsibilities include designing user interactions on websites, developing servers, databases for website\r\nfunctionality, coding for mobile platforms.\r\n</p><p><b>Task Job :</b>\r\n</p><ul><li>Developing front end website architecture.</li><li> Designing user interactions on web pages.\r\n</li><li>Developing back end website applications.</li><li>Creating servers, databases for functionality.</li><li>Ensuring cross-platform optimization for mobile phones. </li><li>Ensuring responsiveness of applications. </li><li>Working alongside graphic designers for web design features. </li><li>Seeing through a project from conception to finished product. </li><li>Designing, developing APIs. </li><li>Meeting both technical, consumer needs. </li><li>Staying abreast of developments in web applications, programming languages.</li></ul><p><b>Key Skill : </b></p><ul><li> Strong organizational </li><li>Project management skills. </li><li>Excellent verbal communication skills. </li><li>Good problem solving skills. </li><li>Attention to detail.\r\nSpecial Skill : </li><li>Proficiency with fundamental front end languages such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript. </li><li>Familiarity with JavaScript frameworks such as Jquery, Angular JS, React, Amber.</li><li>Proficiency with server side languages such as Python, Ruby, Java, PHP, .Net. </li><li>Familiarity with database technology such as MySQL, Oracle, MongoDB.\r\n</li></ul><p><b>Requirement : </b></p><ul><li>Graduated (S1, S2 majoring in IT with IP above 3.25</li><li>2 years experiences as Full Stack Developer <br></li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-13', '2020-08-20 13:21:41'),
(5, 51, 2, 3578, 35, 'marketing-engineer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/marketing-engineer-3333652?fr=21&searchRequestToken=6c4b8417-a801-4c0d-a3fc-6a113db94031&sectionRank=1', 'Marketing Engineer', 'Jalan Mulyosari Tengah V No. 2B - 2C, Rt 001 Rw 006, Kalisari, Mulyorejo, Surabaya, Jatim', '<p><strong>Kriteria :</strong></p><ol><li>Usia Max. 35 Th</li><li>Pendidikan\r\nMin. D3 Teknik Elektro</li><li>Pengalaman kerja sebagai Marketing Engginer Min. 1 Th\r\n</li><li>Menguasai Kelistrikan (arus lemah / arus kuat, motor electical,Breaker LV/MV, softstarter, PLC\r\nserta listrik installasi)</li><li>Memiliki Sertifikat Kompetensi (Diutamakan)</li><li>Mahir\r\nberbahasa Inggris Lisan & Tulisan</li><li>Komunikatif & Kooperatif</li><li>Memiliki Sim A & Sim C</li></ol><p><strong>Tugas Pekerjaan\r\n: </strong></p><ol><li>Membuat jadwal kunjungan dan presentasi kepada customer untuk\r\nmemberikan informasi solusi dan konsultasi mengenai produk secara teknikal</li><li>Membuat\r\nlaporan penjualan</li><li>Melakukan penjualan produk, negosisasi dan follow up PO</li><li>target penjualan yang telah ditetapkan</li><li>Menyusun dan membahas program marketing bersama\r\ntim marketing.</li><li>Menjaga kestabilan dan peningkatan pasar serta kepuasan pelanggan</li><li>Menganalisis antara harga produk dengan penjualan</li><li>Mampu menganalisa dan\r\nmemperbaiki pusat kontrol listrik dan programmable logic controller</li><li>Mampu melakukan\r\ninstallasi listrik dan perbaikannya</li><li>Mampu membaca wiring gambar elektrik dan manual\r\nbook mesin ataupun peralatan elektrik</li><li>Mampu melakukan pemeliharaan rutin dan perbaikan\r\npada peralatan listrik dan menentukan kapan dan apa jenis pemeliharaan kebutuhan</li><li>Mampu\r\nmemecahkan masalah listrik yang rumit</li><li>Mengikuti seminar khusus untuk mengetahui trend\r\nproduk baru</li><li>Mempertahankan relasi / hubungan baik dengan konsumen / klien yang sudah\r\nberjalan, serta memperluas jaringan (networking) bisnis dan membina relasi dengan konsumen / klien\r\nbaru.</li><li>Menganalisis informasi pasar dan peluang potensial bisnis untuk mengembangkan\r\nstrategi penjualan yang inovatif, kreatif, kompetitif, dan profitable.</li><li> Menjaga kerahasiaan\r\n(confidentiality) semua proyek klien / konsumen.</li><li>Mampu bekerja dibawah tekanan dan\r\nmemenuhi tenggat waktu yang tepat</li></ol>', 1, '2020-09-13', '2020-08-20 13:22:03'),
(6, 11, 3, 3171, 31, 'administration-and-client-handler', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/administration-and-client-handler-3336091?fr=J&searchRequestToken=81999b77-e3ac-419a-e227-63fabcdd3fad&sectionRank=1', 'Administration and Client handler', ' Jl. Boulevard Raya Graha Ichsan Arcade III Blok E-1 No.22-23 Sektor VII, Bintaro, Tangerang City, Banten, Indonesia', '<ul> <li>Candidate must possess at least Diploma in Business Studies/Administration/Management or\r\nequivalent.</li> <li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this\r\nposition.</li> <li>Preferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor) specialized in\r\nClerical/Administrative Support or equivalent.</li> <li>Menguasai Microsoft excel dengan baik</li>\r\n<li>Terbiasa Mengurus dokumen berupa : invoice, pajak, dsb</li> <li>Terbisasa mengurus dokumen\r\nperusahaan untuk tender</li> <li>memiliki kemampuan komunikasi dengan klien</li> <li>bisa bekerja\r\ndibawah tekanan dengan deadline yang tingg</li> <li>Menangani hubungan dengan pihak konsumen</li>\r\n<li>bersedia untuk bekerja di hari sabtu</li> <li>siap untuk bekerja didaerah bintaro</li> </ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-09-19', '2020-08-20 13:21:18'),
(7, 11, 4, 3172, 31, 'admin-executive', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/admin-executive-3336090?fr=J&searchRequestToken=81999b77-e3ac-419a-e227-63fabcdd3fad&sectionRank=2', 'Admin Executive', 'Jl. C, TELUK GONG, Pejagalan, Penjaringan Jakarta Utara', '<ul> <li>Candidate must possess at least SMU, Diploma in Business Studies/Administration/Management,\r\nCommerce, Others or equivalent.</li> <li>Required language(s): English</li> <li>At least\r\n2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li> <li>Required\r\nSkill(s): Microsoft Office, Windows OS, Fulfillment</li> <li>Preferably Staff (non-management &\r\nnon-supervisor) specialized in Clerical/Administrative Support or equivalent.</li> </ul>', 1, '2020-09-19', '2020-08-20 13:35:15'),
(8, 11, 5, 3172, 31, 'web-developer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/web-developer-3336087?fr=J&searchRequestToken=81999b77-e3ac-419a-e227-63fabcdd3fad&sectionRank=3', 'WEB DEVELOPER', 'Kelapa Gading - Jakarta Utara', '<strong>Job Requirements:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li> Pendidikan D3/S1 Teknik Informatika/Sistem Informasi/Desain Komunikasi Visual, terbuka untuk lulusan SMK Ilmu Komputer/Multimedia.</li>\r\n <li> Memiliki pengalaman minimal 1 tahun dibidang yang sama.</li>\r\n <li>Melampirkan portofolio desain website atau sistem yang sudah pernah dikerjakan.</li>\r\n <li>Memahami Wordpress, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, PHP, Javascript (Jquery/Angular/Vue)</li>\r\n <li>Mampu mengoperasikan Landingpress, Plugins Elementor, Plugins Siteorigin serta Plugins umum lainnya.</li>\r\n <li>Bekerja on target/deadline.</li>\r\n <li>Dapat berbahasa Inggris dan dengan baik (minimal writing)</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai software desain Adobe Photoshop/Illustrator/XD merupakan nilai tambah</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai SEO lebih diutamakan.</li>\r\n <li>Memiliki Disiplin dan Attitude yang baik (Non-Negotiable).</li>\r\n <li>Siap diposisikan di Kelapa Gading, Jakarta Utara.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div> </div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Job Description & Responsibilities:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Membangun dan memodifikasi website perusahaan.</li>\r\n <li>Membuat landing page untuk kebutuhan Digital Marketing.</li>\r\n <li>Mengoperasikan dan mengatasi kendala yang ada pada website.</li>\r\n <li>Membuat perencanaan, penjadwalan konten, dan melakukan eksekusi atas rencana.</li>\r\n <li>Memonitor, tracking, dan membuat laporan perkembangan masing-masing website.</li>\r\n <li>Aktif melakukan research dan menyediakan insight untuk kemajuan perkembangan perusahaan.</li>\r\n <li>Bekerja sebagai bagian dari tim dan berkolaborasi dengan divisi lain untuk menciptakan ide yang kreatif & inovatif.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2020-09-19', '2020-08-20 13:39:35'),
(9, 25, 6, 3374, 33, 'android-ios-developer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/android-ios-developer-3335417?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=c49bcc7c-ed63-4a9c-a9c5-6604ed025b14&sectionRank=1', 'ANDROID / IOS DEVELOPER', 'Jalan Selomas Raya B21, Semarang', '<p><b>Deskripsi Pekerjaan :</b></p><ul><li>Membuat dokumentasi system</li><li>Membuat Aplikasi sesuai dengan permintaan user </li><li>Testing Program</li></ul><p><b>Persyaratan : </b></p><ul><li>Menguasai Xamarin untuk ios dan android, java, my sql, sql lite, android sdk, ios sdk, swift dan c++ </li><li>Diutamakan berpengalaman dibidangnya (not for fresh graduate)</li><li>Bersedia tugas keluar kota</li><li>Lebih diutamakan menguasai Native Language </li><li>Mampu bekerja secara mandiri atau dalam team</li><li>Mampu bekerja dibawah tekanan dan berorientasi pada target</li><li>Bersedia ditempatkan di Jalan Selomas Raya B21, Semarang</li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-18', '2020-08-20 14:35:28'),
(10, 41, 7, 3215, 32, 'technical-support', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/technical-support-3338216?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=e5e50f3b-34b8-4da1-8c50-e477619ac7b0&sectionRank=1', 'TECHNICAL SUPPORT', 'Jl Karawang Spoor Desa Purwadana, Kec Teluk Jambe, Karawang, West Java 41361, Indonesia', '<p><strong>PURPOSE OF THE JOB</strong></p><p>\r\nEnsures that production processes are in line with group standards and optimized in order to support the yield, cost, quality and services targets</p><p>\r\n\r\n<strong>KEY RESPONSIBILITIES</strong>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Overall activities and process handling:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Setup/Verify if the PCPs are respected and if controls are executed according to SOPs (internal audits)</li>\r\n <li>Put in place tools to monitor processes, measure capabilities (PCP - process control plans) with a focus on calibration ? Track and reacts to results (participate to indicators and targets with production and quality, follow daily indicators)</li>\r\n <li>Train/monitor efficiency of calibrations</li>\r\n <li>Organize and structure problem solving</li>\r\n <li>Prepare training support for processes and calibration with Manufacturing trainer/LOFT, and train operators, Maintenance.</li>\r\n <li>Continuous improvement of the workshop and efficiency, while optimizing consumption of consumables and process time, to permanently improve the manufacturing costs in collaboration with techno clubs.</li>\r\n <li>Organize in coordination with NPI the production and analysis of end-to- end tests in the context of preparation of new offers/product launches.</li>\r\n <li>Contribute to industrial projects/pilot</li>\r\n <li>Introduce new processes from the beginning and assure in lining within permanent process control of defined results, documentation - KPI monitoring, within expected performances</li>\r\n <li>Participate to the budget definition</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>KPIs</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>PCP (indicators/ respect of PCP)</li>\r\n <li>Quality: yields, pareto, defects analysis, capability.</li>\r\n <li>Cost : consumables, equipment, productivity, EER (Equipment Effectiveness Ratio), ...</li>\r\n <li>Machine reliability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong>PROFILE REQUIRED</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>3 to 5 years of work experience within production in any industrial company with the accountability of and responsibility for processes, machinery park and product quality.</li>\r\n <li>Results Oriented and Resilient</li>\r\n <li>In-depth problem solving and Analytical skills</li>\r\n <li>Motivating others, adapts to change, Influencing & Persuading</li>\r\n <li>IT systems depending on the expertise</li>\r\n <li>Bachelor degree of General Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, Industrial Engineering or related field.</li>\r\n <li>Willing to be located in Karawang</li>\r\n</ul></p>', 1, '2020-09-24', '2020-08-25 11:42:15'),
(11, 41, 8, 3216, 33, 'production-supervisor-cikarang', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/production-supervisor-electronics-manufacturing-cikarang-a-55090-3338112?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=e5e50f3b-34b8-4da1-8c50-e477619ac7b0&sectionRank=2', 'Production Supervisor - Electronics Manufacturing - Cikarang (A-55090)', 'Cikarang', '<ul><li><strong><strong>Has working experience managing production line at Electronics Manufacturing\r\ncompany.</strong></strong></li><li><strong><strong>Basic English (to communicate with Japanese\r\nManager\r\nsometime).</strong></strong></li><li><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong><strong>Preferably has\r\nw</strong></strong></strong>orking experience at Japanese\r\ncompany.</strong></strong></strong></li><li><strong><strong>Non-job hopper is\r\np</strong></strong><strong><strong>referable.</strong></strong></li><li><strong><strong><strong>Hold\r\nminimum Bachelor’s degree from any fields.</strong></strong></strong></li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-24', '2020-08-25 11:49:42'),
(12, 41, 9, 3216, 32, 'production-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/production-manager-3337585?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=e5e50f3b-34b8-4da1-8c50-e477619ac7b0&sectionRank=3', 'Production Manager', 'Grand Galaxy City RSA 1 No. 19, Bekasi Selatan', '<ul> <li>Plan and Set Production schedule to achieve target (according to delivery schedule and customer\r\nrequest)</li> <li>Make sure the manufacturing process run effectively and efficiently</li> <li>Manage,\r\ncontrol,  direct ,  motivate and develop the subordinates to achieve targets</li> <li>Set and and\r\nassure the availability of resources to meet the manufacturing process</li> <li>Plan of all equipments\r\nmaintenance schedules to ensure uninterrupted production</li> <li>Coordinate with QC Department for\r\nquality issues</li> <li>Coordinate and liase with internal and external  party for production\r\npurpose</li> <li>Make sure that the work process comply with existing Work Instruction and  SOP\r\n </li> </ul>', 1, '2020-09-23', '2020-08-25 11:55:39'),
(13, 41, 10, 3212, 32, 'kepala-produksi-surimi', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/kepala-produksi-surimi-3337548?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=e5e50f3b-34b8-4da1-8c50-e477619ac7b0&sectionRank=4', 'Kepala Produksi Surimi', 'Jl. By Pass Eretan Kulon No,. 177 Kecamatan Kandanghaur Kab. Indramayu', '<ul><li>Pendidikan minimla D3 Jurusan Perikanan, Teknologi Pangan, atau jurusan yang\r\nrelevan.</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 2 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang pengolahan ikan atau\r\nproduksi surimi.</li><li>Mengerti proses pembuatan surimi</li><li>Mengerti kualitas hasil produksi\r\nsurimi</li><li>Mampu mengontrol kualitas dan kapasitas produksi.</li><li>Siap bekerja dengan sistem\r\nShift.</li><li>Penempatan di Indramayu Jawa Barat.</li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-23', '2020-08-25 12:00:06'),
(14, 41, 11, 3320, 33, 'manufacture-exellence-staff', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/manufacture-exellence-staff-3337917?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3ebdde1a-c5b0-47f4-a0af-e20902cf4a4d&sectionRank=1', 'Manufacture Exellence Staff', 'Jl Krasak Banyuputih RT 09 RW 03 kec. Kalinyamatan, Kab. Jepara', '<ul> <li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya Diploma, Gelar Sarjana di Teknik (Industri) atau setara.</li>\r\n<li>Bahasa yang harus dimiliki: English</li> <li>Pengalaman kerja tidak diperlukan.</li> <li>Kemampuan\r\nyang harus dimiliki: Microsoft Office</li> <li>Lebih disukai Lulusan baru/Pengalaman kerja kurang dari 1\r\ntahun khusus dalam Manufaktur/Operasi Produksi atau setara.</li> </ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-09-24', '2020-08-25 12:07:31'),
(15, 41, 12, 3315, 33, 'qc-supervisor', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/qc-supervisor-3335771?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3ebdde1a-c5b0-47f4-a0af-e20902cf4a4d&sectionRank=2', ' QC SUPERVISOR', 'Jl. Raya Semarang Purwodadi KM 28, Tegowanu, Grobogan', '<p xss=removed><b>Tugas & Tanggung jawab :</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li xss=removed>Merencanakan jadwal  kegiatan QCQA sesuai dengan target kerja dan pelaksanaan proses\r\nproduksi</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Mengkoordinasikan,mengawasi, dan mengatur personil dan\r\nseluruh anggota QCQA sesuai pelaksanaan produksi dan target kerja yang telah ditentukan</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Melakukan pengawasan dan fungsi kontrol serta proses QC untuk bahan baku,\r\nproduk setengah jadi dan barang jadi secara keseluruhan tercatat dalam rekaman mutu dan dilaksanakan\r\nsesuai dengan standard SOP yang berlaku. </li></ul><pstyle><p></p><p xss=removed><b>Kualifikasi:</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p><ul>\r\n<li xss=removed>Usia maksimal 40 tahun</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Pendidikan minimal D1 atau yang sederajat</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Memiliki pengalaman minimal 3 tahun sebagai QC Supervisor/Leader di perusahaan garmen</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Menguasai bahan baku, proses produksi dan produk jadi dari sisi kualitas</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Memahami teknis dalam penjahitan dan teknologi mesin jahit</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Memiliki kemampuan serta kepemimpinan efektif & efisien</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Mampu memberikan analisa dan keputusan terhadap permasalahan yang menyangkut masalah kualitas</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Mampu menangani complain dari buyer/customer/rekanan dengan baik</li><li xss=removed>Mampu beradaptasi dengan baik dalam lingkungan kerja yang memiliki deadline yang ketat</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Mampu bekerja dengan tingkat pressure tinggi</li>\r\n<li xss=removed>Mampu berkomunikasi dengan bahasa Inggris (Oral and Written)</li><li xss=removed>Bersedia ditempatkan di Tegowanu, Grobogan</li>\r\n</ul><p></p></pstyle>', 1, '2020-09-18', '2020-08-25 12:16:43'),
(16, 41, 13, 3322, 33, 'kepala-departemen-bahan-baku', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/kepala-departemen-bahan-baku-3335500?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3ebdde1a-c5b0-47f4-a0af-e20902cf4a4d&sectionRank=3', 'KEPALA DEPARTEMEN BAHAN BAKU', 'Jl. Anton Sujarwo 117 Semarang', '<ul><li xss=removed>S1 TEKNIK MESIN ( JURUSAN METALURGI LEBIH DI\r\nUTAMAKAN )</li><li xss=removed>MENGUASAI GAMBAR TEHNIK</li><li xss=removed>MAMPU MENGANALISA PROBLEM SOLVING</li><li xss=removed>MEMILIKI KEPRIBADIAN  DAN KEMAMPUAN BERKOMUNIKASI YANG\r\nBAIK</li><li xss=removed>MEMILIKI MOTIVASI YANG TINGGI DAN DAPAT\r\nBEKERJA SECARA TIM MAUPUN INDIVIDU</li><li xss=removed>DISIPLIN DAN\r\nBERTANGGUNG JAWAB, MAMPU MENGATASI MASALAH</li><li xss=removed>BERPENGALAMAN MINIMAL 3 TAHUN</li><li xss=removed>USIA\r\nMAKSIMAL 40 TAHUN</li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-18', '2020-08-25 12:20:58'),
(17, 53, 14, 5171, 51, 'management-development-program-mdp-bali', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/management-development-program-mdp-bali-3340284?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=82e33165-c7aa-4df3-a389-ef49c0249554&sectionRank=1', 'Management Development Program (MDP) - Bali', 'Jl. H. Agus Salim, Central Jakarta No 45, Menteng, Jakarta 10340, Indonesia', '<strong>Requirement</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>University fresh graduates with minimum Bachelor Degree from any major</li>\r\n <li>Must earn a minimum latest GPA of 2.75 out of 4.00</li>\r\n <li>Active in various organizations, leadership activities and other extracurricular</li>\r\n <li>Experience in having/managing small business would be a plus point</li>\r\n <li>Maximum age 25</li>\r\n <li>Owned & able to drive motorcycle</li>\r\n <li>Bali</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2020-09-26', '2020-08-27 20:45:49'),
(18, 53, 15, 5171, 51, 'marketing-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/marketing-manager-3340273?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=82e33165-c7aa-4df3-a389-ef49c0249554&sectionRank=2', 'Marketing Manager', 'Jl Prof I B Mantra No 25 Kesiman, Denpasar Bali, Indonesia', '<strong>ESSENTIAL DUTIES & RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Define Target Markets and Target Groups (Market segmentation).</li>\r\n <li>Get Market Research Data that support this market segmentation.</li>\r\n <li>Define for each Target Market and Target Group the product portfolio.</li>\r\n <li>Propose the preferred marketing channels to reach these target markets.</li>\r\n <li>Develop a marketing strategy and strategic objectives for each Product/Market combination.</li>\r\n <li>Develop an event strategy with clear objectives as part of the marketing strategy.</li>\r\n <li>Develop a social media strategy and communication strategy with clear objectives as part of the marketing strategy.</li>\r\n <li>Define the different brands and develop a clear brand strategy.</li>\r\n <li>Develop the overall Marketing Plan (includes the tactics and actions) together with a Budget Plan.</li>\r\n <li>Lead the execution of the marketing strategy.</li>\r\n <li>Lead the participation in events on behalf of the company.</li>\r\n <li>Manage the execution of event participation, including stand development, branding, and development of promotional materials.</li>\r\n <li>Execute the brand strategy and develop further the company’s brand image by targeted interventions.</li>\r\n <li>Measure brand awareness with the various target groups and take appropriate actions to enhance awareness.</li>\r\n <li>Work as a team (hand in glove) with Sales and Account Management to further strengthen the company’s presence in the different markets.</li>\r\n <li>Lead the execution of the Social Media Strategy (with appropriate (3rd) parties.</li>\r\n <li>Measure the success of the various Social Media Channels and adjust where needed.</li>\r\n <li>Take part in a cross functional team of Sales/Account Manager and New Product Development Manager to initiate and develop new products</li>\r\n <li>Manage market research to gain insight in market trends, business environment, customers, products, and competitors.</li>\r\n <li>Use Market Research as input to adjust the marketing/product strategies and share with Sales and Account Management.</li>\r\n <li>Monitor on a monthly basis the effectiveness of execution of the Marketing Strategy and Marketing Plan (the actions) against the targets (Strategic Objectives translated into KPI’s).</li>\r\n <li>Adjust the Marketing Strategy based on Market Research Data and Realization data.</li>\r\n <li>Coach and mentor the team to enable them to maximize performance and support learning and development of team members.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<p><strong>CORE COMPETENCIES / KNOWLEDGE & SKILL:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Marketing Strategy</li>\r\n <li>Social Media and Communications Strategy</li>\r\n <li>Marketing Management</li>\r\n <li>Brand Management</li>\r\n <li>Event Management</li>\r\n <li>Market Research – knowledge level only</li>\r\n <li>Public Relations – knowledge level only</li>\r\n <li>Budgeting</li>\r\n <li>Collaboration</li>\r\n <li>Drive for Results</li>\r\n <li>Innovation & Change</li>\r\n <li>Communication</li>\r\n <li>Operational Decision Making</li>\r\n <li>Managing People</li>\r\n <li>Customer Centricity</li>\r\n <li>Integrity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>QUALIFICATIONS:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Bachelor’s Degree in Marketing or related field.</li>\r\n <li>Minimum experience of 5 years in the same filed.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1, '2020-09-26', '2020-08-27 20:56:09'),
(19, 7, 16, 3172, 31, 'supervisor', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/supervisor-tax-accounting-3341991?fr=J&src=2&searchRequestToken=44fe4447-41e6-4525-c03a-236733289eee&sectionRank=1', 'Supervisor Tax Accounting', 'Jakarta Utara', '<p><b>Persyaratan:</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya Gelar Sarjana di Akuntansi.</li>\r\n <li>?Kandidat harus memiliki Brevet A & B</li>\r\n <li>Setidaknya memiliki 5 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi ini.</li>\r\n <li>Lebih disukai Supervisor/Koordinator khusus dalam Audit/Pajak atau setara.</li>\r\n <li>Usia 28 - 35 tahun</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai computer dan program Ms. Office (Ms. Word, Excel, dan Power Point)</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai perpajakan beserta program pendukungnya (Efaktur, E-SPT, dll)</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai program MYOB dan Accurate</li>\r\n <li>Menguasai pembuatan laporan keuangan, pajak, kas, hutang, piutang, dll</li>\r\n <li>Teliti dan cekatan dalam bekerja</li>\r\n <li>Dapat memimpin dan bekerja sama dalam team</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-09-30', '2020-08-31 12:19:27'),
