(21, 11, 18, 3201, 32, 'sales-admin', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-admin-3342192?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=25774f50-5365-4505-bba0-c014bdecf6aa&sectionRank=4', 'Sales Admin', 'Jl Marcedez 324, Wanaherang, Gunung Putri, West Java, Indonesia 16820', '<p><b>Tanggung Jawab Utama :</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Bertanggung jawab melakukan support atas segala kebutuhan administrasi sales & marketing.</li>\r\n <li>Membuat dan mengirimkan Quotations kepada customer.</li>\r\n <li>Dapat berkomunikasi dengan baik kepada customer (lisan/Tulisan) atasan langsung/ Director/ Management.</li>\r\n <li>Mengelola segala kebutuhan promosi dan komunikasi baik hard maupun softcopy</li>\r\n <li>Melakukan support dalam administrasi tender.</li>\r\n <li>Membuat laporan dan notulen (Note Of Meeting) serta update Sales Forecast.</li>\r\n <li>Membuat Report Harian kepada Manager / atasan langsung</li>\r\n <li>Mengerjakan pekerjaan sales admin lainnya.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Spesifikasi Kandidat :</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Pendidikan minimal D3 Teknik/Management/Ekonomi/ Administasi/ Sekretaris.</strong></li>\r\n <li>Pengalaman minimal 2 tahun diposisi yang sama. <strong>(diutamakan pengalaman di Manufacturing, Oil & Gas).</strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Mengerti dan paham sistem management mutu (ISO 9001, API – bersertifikat lebih disukai)</strong></li>\r\n <li>Dapat berkomunikasi yang baik dengan jaringan dalam perusahaan (lisan maupun tulisan)</li>\r\n <li><strong>Menguasai Ms. Office </strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Menguasai Bahasa Inggris (lisan dan tulisan)</strong></li>\r\n <li>Menyiapkan, melengkapi dan <strong>selalu up to date dengan persyaratan tender</strong></li>\r\n <li>Filling dokumen serta mengerti dasar pembukuan dan keuangan</li>\r\n <li>Mampu bekerja dibawah tekanan dan schedule yang ketat serta kerja efektif dan optimal</li>\r\n <li>Berpenampilan baik (sikap dan perilaku)</li>\r\n <l>Penempatan di Wanaherang Gunung Putri Bogor\r\n <li>Berdomilisi di sekitar JABODERTABEK – lebih disukasi dekat dengan lokasi bekerja.</li>\r\n</l></ul>', 1, '2020-09-30', '2020-09-01 14:11:31'),
(22, 11, 19, 3201, 32, 'admin-head-adh', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/admin-head-adh-3331929?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=25774f50-5365-4505-bba0-c014bdecf6aa&sectionRank=5', 'ADMIN HEAD (ADH)', 'Bekasi (Jawa Barat), Bogor (Jawa Barat), Karawang (Jawa Barat), Purwakarta (Jawa Barat), Sukabumi (Jawa Barat), Tangerang (Banten)', '<ul><li>Usia Maksimal 40\r\ntahun.</li><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya Diploma, Gelar Sarjana di bidang\r\napapun.</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 2 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi ini,\r\ndiutamakan yang memiliki pengalaman bekerja di <strong>distibutor consumer\r\ngoods.</strong></li><li>Lebih disukai Supervisor/Koordinator khusus dalam Clerical/Staf Admin atau\r\nsetara.</li><li>Mampu mengoperasikan Ms. Office terutama Ms. Excel.</li><li>Memiliki kemampuan\r\nberhitung, analisa dan logika yang baik.</li><li>proaktif dan cepat tanggap.</li><li>mampu bekerja di\r\nbawah tekanan.</li><li>memiliki interpersonal skill dan komunikasi yang baik.</li><li>bersedia di\r\ntempatkan di seluruh cabang perusahaan (bogor, sukabumi, purwakarta, karawang, bekasi,\r\ntangerang,serang).</li></ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-09-11', '2020-09-01 14:16:49'),
(23, 16, 20, 3174, 31, 'creative-design-coordinator', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/creative-design-coordinator-3342872?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3f7a433f-54cd-4c8c-e4ff-ca2771bcac40&sectionRank=2', 'Creative Design Coordinator', 'Jl. Prof. Dr. Satrio, Jakarta Selatan, Jakarta, Indonesia', '<p><b>Job Summary</b></p>\r\n<p> We\'re looking for a talent who have an in-depth understanding of advertising and composition, make a creative and interesting piece that helps our product stands out. You have to supervise and ensuring the creation of visual concepts and designs (POS, POP, marketing collateral, brochures, catalysis, etc.) is done according to the specified deadline. If you are expert at creating eye-catching visuals then we\'d love to hear from you.</p>\r\n<p><b>This duties include, but not limited to;</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Supervise the process design and create traditional print marketing materials (<strong>Brochures, catalogue,P-O-P, P-O-S, </strong>etc).</li>\r\n <li>Ensure team are able to create images that identify a product or convey a message.</li>\r\n <li>Give recommendation on selecting colors, images, text style, and layout.</li>\r\n <li>Communicate the design to Product Marketing Head.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Job Requirements;</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor\'s Degree in Art/Design/Creative Multimedia or equivalent.</li>\r\n <li>Able to operate Adobe creative suite (Photoshop,In-Design,Illustrator) and Microsoft Office.</li>\r\n <li>Maximum 35 Years old.</li>\r\n <li>At least 5 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>\r\n</ul> ', 1, '2020-10-01', '2020-09-01 14:27:05'),
(24, 16, 21, 3171, 31, 'desainer-grafis', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/desain-grafis-marketplace-ecommerce-3342859?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3f7a433f-54cd-4c8c-e4ff-ca2771bcac40&sectionRank=3', 'DESAIN GRAFIS Marketplace ECommerce', 'Jakarta Pusat (Jakarta Raya)', '<ul> <li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya\r\nSMA, Diploma, Gelar Sarjana di bidang apapun.</li> <li>Bahasa yang harus dimiliki: Bahasa\r\nIndonesia</li> <li>Setidaknya memiliki 1 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi\r\nini.</li> <li>Kemampuan yang harus dimiliki: menguasai berbagai marketplace, edit dan design, photoshop,\r\nsocial media, instagram, promosi marketplace, kreatif, Desain grafis, E-Commerce</li> <li>Lebih disukai\r\nPegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor) khusus dalam Seni/Kreatif/Desain Grafis atau setara.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-10-01', '2020-09-01 14:32:08'),
(25, 16, 22, 3173, 31, 'editor-video', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/editor-video-3342823?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3f7a433f-54cd-4c8c-e4ff-ca2771bcac40&sectionRank=4', ' EDITOR VIDEO', 'Jakarta Barat (Jakarta Raya) - Soho Capital', '<ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya D3 atau S1 Jurusan Broadcaster, DKV atau Multimedia.</li><li>Usia Maksimal 28 Tahun.</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 2 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi ini.</li><li>Kemampuan yang harus dimiliki: Adobe Premiere, After Effect, Photoshop, Illustrator, Cinema 4D.</li><li>Lebih disukai Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor) khusus dalam Seni/Kreatif/Desain Grafis atau setara.</li><li>Menguasai aplikasi Adobe Premiere, After Effect, Photoshop, Illustrator dan juga Cinema 4D.</li><li>Mampu mengoperasikan kamera DSLR dan Mirrorless.</li><li>Cekatan, inisiatif dan fast learning.</li><li>Mampu bekerja di bawah tekanan.</li><li>Memiliki kemampuan dalam penyesuaian editing.</li><li>Memiliki kreatifitas dan imajinasi yang tinggi.</li></ul><div><strong>Deskripsi pekerjaan:</strong></div><ul><li>Merekam video, baik event maupun produk</li><li>Melakukan sameday editing dan project editing sesuai dengan deadline yang sudah ditentukan</li><li>Membuat animasi 2D seperti video infografis.</li></ul>\r\n', 1, '2020-10-01', '2020-09-01 14:38:21'),
(26, 16, 23, 3172, 31, 'creative-graphic-design-supervisor', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/creative-graphic-design-supervisor-3342688?fr=J&src=12&searchRequestToken=3f7a433f-54cd-4c8c-e4ff-ca2771bcac40&sectionRank=5', ' Creative Graphic Design Supervisor', 'Agung Sedayu Group Tower, Jl. Pantai Indah Kapuk Boulevard - Kawasan Pantai Indah Kapuk, Kel. Kamal Muara, Kec. Penjaringan, Jakarta Utara', '', 1, '2020-10-01', '2020-09-01 14:50:55'),
(27, 23, 24, 3174, 31, 'hubungan-masyarakat', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/public-relation-3343303?fr=21&searchRequestToken=898668a9-1a18-452b-d455-eda1d8914055&sectionRank=1', 'Hubungan Masyarakat', 'Cibis Office Tower, Jalan Raya Cilandak Kko, South Jakarta City, Special Capital Region of Jakarta, Indonesia', '<b>Responsibilities:</b>\r\n<ul><li>Market analysis and development.</li><li>Coordinating the overall of communication both internal & external including develop communication content in Bahasa & English.</li><li>Handle sponsorship and internal company event.</li><li>Maintain relation with key media including media event & media monitoring related with article both company and competitor.</li><li>Manage PR section plan & budgeting.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><b>Requirements:</b></p>\r\n<ul><li>Age 25 – 30 years old.</li><li>Minimal S1 Communication/Public Relation with minimal 2 years’ experience in Public Relation,</li><li>Able to work under pressure both individual and team.</li><li>Honest, Responsible, highly motivate and target oriented.</li></ul><div> </div><div><div><strong>General Requirements</strong>:</div><ul><li>Minimum GPA 3.00.</li><li>Excellent knowledge of Public Relation.</li><li>Fluent in English and Bahasa (Madarin or Japanese is a plus).</li><li>Pleasant interpersonal skill, excellent communication skills both verbal and written.Proficient in both PC and Mac, MS. Office Applications.</li><li>Strong interpersonal relationships skills.</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-01', '2020-09-02 22:02:23'),
(28, 48, 25, 1271, 12, 'marketing-staff', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/marketing-staff-medan-3344594?fr=21&src=12&searchRequestToken=97266bb6-5213-4f06-f041-a7f291e828ad&sectionRank=1', 'Marketing Staff Medan', 'Sinar Mas Land Plaza 4th Floor, Jalan Diponegoro No. 18, Medan 20152', '<p><b>Main responsibilities:</b></p>\r\n<ul><li>Assess a market condition and identify a sales opportunities.</li><li>Achieve business / commercial target</li><li>Build and maintain a strong relationship with customers and supplierr</li><li>Handle the financing process from initial stage until end of contract</li></ul>\r\n<p><b>General Requirements:</b></p>\r\n<ul><li>Minimum Bachelor Degree from any discipline with GPA > 3</li><li>Fresh graduate, min. age 22 years old</li><li>Has a strong interpersonal skills and good teamwork</li><li>Has a excellent negotiation skills</li><li>Has a excellent communication skills; both in writing and verbal communication</li><li>Has a strong analytical skill</li><li>Highly motivated and positive attitude</li></ul>', 1, '2020-10-03', '2020-09-03 14:08:05'),
(29, 48, 26, 1271, 12, 'qa-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/qa-manager-aquaculture-company-medan-3342555?fr=21&src=12&searchRequestToken=97266bb6-5213-4f06-f041-a7f291e828ad&sectionRank=2', 'QA Manager - Aquaculture Company - Medan', 'Gedung Pacific Place Lt 12, SCBD Jalan Jendral Sudiran Kav 52 - 53', '<p>Our client is looking for a QA Manager who will provide leadership, direction and execution of all quality and food safety functions at the plant level. This person will ensure all products produced meet or exceed all customer, regulatory and company requirements.</p>\r\n<p><b>Client Details</b></p>\r\n<p><br>Our client is a leading aquaculture company located in Medan.</p>\r\n<p><br><b>Description</b></p>\r\n<div xss=removed><br>• Manage all activities of the Quality Assurance/Food Safety department in a manner which results in consistent</div><div xss=removed>  food safety results as measured through the company matrix and regulatory mandates.<br>• Develop, document and implement Quality Assurance and HACCP processes/ procedures to monitor incoming</div><div xss=removed>  raw materials, in-process and finished products to ensure compliance to all regulatory and company</div><div xss=removed>  requirements and specifications<br>• Ensure that the Quality Assurance department is properly organised, staffed and trained to meet and achieve</div><div xss=removed>  plant and departmental goals<br>• Perform as plant contact person for sales and customer issues<br>• Manage the activities of the Quality Assurance department in a manner that keeps plant and upper management</div><div xss=removed>  fully informed on any issues and assists in achieving quality/food safety goals<br>• Develop a professional working relationship and act as a plant liaison with USDA staff.<br>• Enforce corporate food safety and quality programs and maintain the required documentation and provide</div><div xss=removed>  continuing education of plant associates as required.</div><div><br><strong>Profile</strong></div><div xss=removed><br>• Bachelor of Science or Engineering degree from four-year university<br>• At least four to five years related experience and/or training; or equivalent combination of education and</div><div xss=removed>   experience.<br>• Certified in BRC, FDA, GMP, HACCP and FSMS-ISO the latest version 22000, QMS ISO 9001 and laboratory</div><div xss=removed>  microbiology chemistry based on ISO 17025<br>• At least three years of working experience as a QA Manager in food manufacturing industry<br>• Knowledge and understanding of food processing required<br>• Must have or complete certification status as Certified Food Safety Manager or equivalent<br>• Must have experience in frozen food<br>• Must be fluent in English (written and spoken)<br>• Understanding of management principles and team concepts<br>• Understanding of further processing is a plus<br>• Must be willing to relocate to Medan</div><div><br><b>Job Offer</b></div><div xss=removed><b><br>• Working with multinational company<br>• Good remuneration package<br>• Good working environment</b></div><p><b><br>To apply online please click the \'Apply\' button below. For a confidential discussion about this role please contact Della Fauzan.</b></p>', 1, '2020-10-03', '2020-09-03 14:15:11'),
(30, 50, 27, 3175, 31, 'sales-promotor-consultant', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-promotor-consultant-bahan-bangunan-cat-area-pemalang-yogya-3335296?fr=21&src=12&searchRequestToken=6fa0d672-887e-49ce-bd15-1ab0689e9457&sectionRank=1', 'SALES PROMOTOR CONSULTANT BAHAN BANGUNAN (CAT)', 'Jl. Suci No.84, Ciracas, Jakarta Timur', '<p>SALES PROMOTOR CONSULTANT BAHAN BANGUNAN (CAT) AREA PEMALANG & YOGYA<br></p>\r\n<p><b>Responsibilities :</b></p><ul><li>Promosi , selling mencapai target maksimal</li><li>Memberikan panduan dalam penggunaan Product</li><li>Mengcollect data contact Kepala Tukang dan kontraktor</li></ul><div><strong>Requirements :</strong></div><ul><li>Usia 20 – 33 minimal tahun</li><li>Pendidikan minimal SMA/SMK sederaja</li><li>Experience sebagai sales/promotor di perusahaan Cat (Paints) minimal 1 tahun, Sales FMCG/bahan bangunan minimal 2 tahun</li><li>Bersedia kerja mobile</li><li>Sales & Target Oriented</li><li>Komunikasi dan kemampuan menjual yang baik</li><li>Pekerja keras, fisik & mental fisik kuat</li><li>Ulet, gigih, sabar, dan memiliki integritas yang baik.</li><li>Memiliki SIM C</li></ul><p>AREA : PEMALANG</p>', 1, '2020-09-18', '2020-09-06 14:29:45'),
(31, 50, 28, 3471, 33, 'sales-manager-centrak-area', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-manager-central-area-3332820?fr=21&src=12&searchRequestToken=6fa0d672-887e-49ce-bd15-1ab0689e9457&sectionRank=2', 'Sales Manager Central Area', 'Graha Mobisel, Kalibata, Jakarta, Indonesia', '<ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor\'s Degree, Master\'s Degree/Post Graduate Degree in Engineering (Civil), Business Studies/Administration/Management, Economics or equivalent.</li><li>At least 5 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li><li><strong>Required Skill(s): english, communicative, leadership</strong></li><li>Preferably Manager/Assistant Manager specialized in Sales - Retail/General or equivalent.</li><li>Hard worker and target oriented, good negotiating</li><li><strong>Have driving lisence A and C</strong></li><li><strong>Good communication in English</strong></li><li><strong>Business and Concrete knowledge is a must</strong></li><li><strong>Placement area : Yogya, Semarang, and Solo</strong></li></ul>\r\n<p><strong>Mainjob :</strong></p>\r\n<ul><li>Plan, organize, develop, and control sales activity to achieve volume sales target also sell the readmix concrete</li><li>Set, evaluate and socialize the strategic objectives of concrete marketing as well as design : the strategy, policy, annual planning and implementation system</li><li>Clear the outstanding payment<strong> </strong></li></ul>', 1, '2020-09-12', '2020-09-06 14:37:51'),
(32, 53, 29, 1871, 18, 'sales-lampung', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-lampung-3346048?fr=J&src=5&searchRequestToken=aaa98453-f82d-4a64-e7db-4a99caa3cf47&sectionRank=1', 'SALES LAMPUNG', 'Jl. Tembesu 4 No.30 RT01/RW01, Campang Raya, Sukabumi, Bandar Lampung, Indonesia', '<ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya SMA maximal S1.</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 2 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi ini.</li><li>Kemampuan yang harus dimiliki: Microsoft Office, microsoft excel</li><li>Lebih disukai Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor) khusus dalam [Specialization] atau setara.</li><li>Jujur dan Teliti</li><li>Update Stock Barang</li><li>Cek Stock Barang</li><li>Filling Dokumen</li><li>Siap bekerja dengan cepat</li></ul>', 1, '2020-10-05', '2020-09-06 14:43:55'),
(35, 53, 30, 1871, 18, 'staff-laboratorium', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/staff-laboratorium-quality-control-lampung-3345673?fr=J&src=5&searchRequestToken=aaa98453-f82d-4a64-e7db-4a99caa3cf47&sectionRank=2', 'STAFF LABORATORIUM & QUALITY CONTROL - LAMPUNG', 'Jl. Raya Semarang-Kendal km 10.5, Kaliwungu, Central Java, Indonesia', '<p>DIBUTUHKAN SEGERA</p>\r\n<p><b>STAFF QUALITY CONTROL - LAMPUNG</b></p>\r\n<p>persyaratan:</p>\r\n<p>- Pendidikan minimal SMK/ D3 Kimia</p><p>- Teliti, tepat waktu</p><p>- Pengalaman sebagai staff Lab / QC Pabrik </p><p>- Bersedia bekerja secara shift</p><p>- Fresh graduate are welcome</p><p>- Penempatan <b>LAMPUNG</b></p>', 1, '2020-10-04', '2020-09-06 14:48:42'),
(36, 8, 31, 3174, 31, 'custody-atm', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/custody-atm-3344010?fr=J&src=16&searchRequestToken=cd799212-59bf-4fa0-fcbe-44976eaff1df&sectionRank=21', 'Custody ATM', 'Jalan Dukuh Patra V / 56 Menteng Dalam, South Jakarta, Jakarta, Indonesia', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div xss=removed><strong>PT Abacus Cash Solution</strong></div><div xss=removed>Kami adalah  sebuah perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang jasa pendukung kegiatan perbankan yang didirikan di Jakarta pada tahun 2002. ACS merupakan bagian dari anak Perusahaan Dana Pensiun BCA. Sejak berdirinya, ACS telah berhasil menjadi perusahaan yang terbaik dengan mengukuhkan reputasi yang terpercaya dan dapat diandalkan oleh Pelanggan. ACS didirikan untuk menjawab kebutuhan masyarakat dan dunia perbankan akan jasa Pengelolaan Uang Tunai (Cash Management Services), Cash In Transit dan ATM Replenishment. http://www.abacuscash.co.id/</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Tugas dan Tanggung Jawab :</div><ul><li xss=removed>Mengisi mesin ATM dengan cepat, tepat, benar, dan jujur (Layanan pengisian dan/atau penggantian uang pada mesin ATM ini dilakukan secara terintegrasi selama 24 jam untuk meminimalisir downtime mesin ATM, dan membebaskan petugas bank melakukan tugas tersebut).</li></ul><div xss=removed>Kualifikasi :</div><ul><li><div xss=removed>Kualifikasi ;</div></li><li xss=removed>Usia maksimal 30 tahun</li><li xss=removed>Pendidikan minimal SMA/SMK semua jurusan</li><li xss=removed>Mampu Mengendarai Mobil dan Memiliki SIM A/B dan SIM C</li><li xss=removed>Bersedia Bekerja Shift</li><li xss=removed>Sehat Jasmani dan Rohani</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div></div>', 1, '2020-10-02', '2020-09-06 14:53:11'),
(37, 8, 31, 3174, 31, 'cash-proccessing-center', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/cash-processing-center-3342980?fr=J&src=16&searchRequestToken=cd799212-59bf-4fa0-fcbe-44976eaff1df&sectionRank=22', 'Cash Processing Center', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div><strong>PT Abacus Cash Solution</strong></div><div>Kami adalah  sebuah perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang jasa pendukung kegiatan perbankan yang didirikan di Jakarta pada tahun 2002. ACS merupakan bagian dari anak Perusahaan Dana Pensiun BCA.Sejak berdirinya, ACS telah berhasil menjadi perusahaan yang terbaik dengan mengukuhkan reputasi yang terpercaya dan dapat diandalkan oleh Pelanggan. ACS didirikan untuk menjawab kebutuhan masyarakat dan dunia perbankan akan jasa Pengelolaan Uang Tunai (Cash Management Services), Cash In Transit dan ATM Replenishment. http://www.abacuscash.co.id/</div><div> </div><div><div><strong>CASH PROCESSING CENTER</strong></div></div><div><div> </div><div>Tugas dan Pekerjaan ;</div><ol><li>Melakukan proses perhitungan dan penyortiran</li><li>Mempersiapkan permintaan kebutuhan Klien sesuai dengan Surat Perintah Kerja yang diterima</li><li>Mampu bekerja dengan target penyelesaian</li><li>Mengikuti proses kerja sesuai dengan ketentuan Perusahaan</li></ol><div> </div><div>Kualifikasi ;</div><ol><li>Usia maksimal 30 tahun</li><li>Pendidikan minimal SMA/SMK semua jurusan</li><li>Bersedia Bekerja Shift</li><li>Sehat Jasmani dan Rohani</li></ol></div></div></div>', 1, '2020-10-02', '2020-09-06 14:55:11'),
(39, 8, 32, 3515, 35, 'production-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/production-manager-3344036?fr=J&src=16&searchRequestToken=cd799212-59bf-4fa0-fcbe-44976eaff1df&sectionRank=23', 'Production Manager', 'Jl. Raya Bringin Bendo No. 42 Taman-Sidoarjo - Jawa Timur - Indonesia', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>S1 graduates from any engineering faculty with a minimum 5-year working experience as a manager in a manufacturing company of at least 300 workers</li><li>Knowledgable to cost evaluation, performance evaluation, root cause analysis, and other management tools</li><li>Cost consciousness and customer focus attitude is a must</li><li>Willing to be placed in either Sepanjang, Sidoarjo or Jasem, Mojosari, Mojokerto sites</li><li>Ready for immediate placement</li><li>Several positions are available</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-02', '2020-09-07 15:24:19'),
(40, 62, 33, 3276, 32, 'fisikawan-medis', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/fisikawan-medis-3340198?fr=J&searchRequestToken=3cb7b95c-4b99-4d5d-bfeb-57862bd58cd3&sectionRank=1', 'FISIKAWAN MEDIS', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div xss=removed>Bertanggung jawab di pelayanan rumah sakit dalam jaminan kualitas/kontrol kualitas peralatan sumber radiasi, pengukuran keluaran berkas radiasi, dan menghitung dosis radiasi serta meneliti keakurasian sistem, metode dan peralatan yang dipakai dalam menjaga keakuratan dosis radiasi.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>KUALIFIKASI :</strong></div><ul><li xss=removed>Pendidikan minimal S1 dari jurusan <strong>Fisika Medis</strong></li><li xss=removed>Fresh graduate dipersilahkan untuk apply</li><li xss=removed>Memiliki STR yang masih berlaku</li><li xss=removed>Teliti serta memiliki semangat bekerja yang baik</li><li xss=removed>Sehat jasmani & rohani</li><li xss=removed>Mampu me-manage pekerjaan dengan baik</li><li xss=removed>Bersedia bekerja full time di Mitra Keluarga Depok & Mitra Keluarga Cibubur</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-09-26', '2020-09-06 15:02:56');
