(57, 33, 49, 3174, 31, 'construction-engineer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/construction-engineer-3347949?fr=J&searchRequestToken=a2af3a02-3d86-4297-c3d0-a200d5a919bb&sectionRank=2', 'Construction Engineer', 'Jl Margasatwa No 111 Pondok Labu Jakarta Selatan 12450', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Qualification</strong> :</div><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor\'s Degree in Engineering (Civil), Engineering (Industrial), Engineering (Mechanical), Engineering (Petroleum/Oil/Gas) or equivalent.</li><li>Required language(s): English</li><li>At least 8 Year(s) of working experience in the project and construction engineering on onshore and offshore Oil & Gas industries..</li><li>Preferably Supervisor/Coordinator specialized in Engineering - Oil/Gas or equivalent.</li><li>Provide technical support to Senior Construction Engineer and Project Manager and assist them with project planning and scheduling.</li><li>Have excellent engineering, interpersonal, planning, and scheduling skills as well as superior written and oral communication abilities.</li><li>Have a good understanding of all applicable code standards, and specifications.</li></ul><div><strong>Responsibilities :</strong></div><ul><li>Review technical aspects of the construction procedures and methods to ensure compliance and satisfy to the applicable international standards and ENI standards.</li><li>Responsible for the development of the construction engineering documents (e.g shop drawings, material lists, test packages, heavy-lift analysis, load out, etc) functional test procedures, offshore/onshore installation job cards, and as-built drawings.</li><li>Assist Senior Construction Engineer with progress, trend analysis, recovery planning.</li><li>Supervision of the site supervisor during construction activities.</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-08', '2020-09-08 20:41:32'),
