(76, 30, 66, 3509, 35, 'ehs-staff', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/ehs-staff-jember-jawa-timur-3349404?fr=J&searchRequestToken=92de2613-de55-4935-b0bc-220d7ac7d4d1&sectionRank=3', 'EHS Staff', '', '<h2 class=\"job-ads-h2\"><strong xss=removed>Persyaratan dan Kualifikasi</strong><br><span class=\"icon-edit-pencil\"></span></h2><div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\">\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Pendidikan min. D3/S1 Jurusan Teknik Lingkungan / K3 / Teknik Industri / Kesehatan Masyarakat / Teknologi Pangan</li>\r\n <li>Pengalaman bekerja min. 2 tahun sebagai EHS Staff, khususnya di perkebunan atau industri makanan</li>\r\n <li>Memiliki pemahaman yang baik terkait ISO 14001, ISO 45001, OHSAS 18001, ISO 22000, HACCP dan memiliki sertifikat AK3 Umum</li>\r\n <li>Bersedia ditempatkan di wilayah operasional perusahaan khususnya di <strong>Jember, Jawa Timur.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Garis Besar Pekerjaan</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Mengidentifikasi potensi bahaya dan dampak lingkungan untuk meminimalkan resiko yang dapat menyebabkan kerugian terhadap perusahaan dan karyawan</li>\r\n <li>Merencanakan Improvement Program EHS Management System sesuai perkembangan peraturan pemerintah RI</li>\r\n <li>Mengidentifikasi dan merencanakan kebutuhan Training Safety untuk meningkatkan kompetensi staff dan karyawan</li>\r\n <li>Mengkoordinasikan implementasi Environment, Health, and Safety Management System kepada setiap departemen untuk menekan angka kecelakaan dan penyakit akibat kerja seminimal mungkin</li>\r\n <li>Mengontrol penerapan EHS Management System pada setiap departemen</li>\r\n <li>Mengevaluasi/mengaudit penerapan EHS Management System di setiap departemen</li>\r\n <li>Mengontrol pemenuhan dokumen EHS Management System untuk memastikan program dan ketentuan keselamatan dijalankan sesuai peraturan yang berlaku</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div></div></div>', 1, '2020-10-10', '2020-09-10 21:13:55'),
(77, 66, 67, 3173, 31, 'legal-senior-officer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/legal-senior-officer-3349401?fr=J&searchRequestToken=92de2613-de55-4935-b0bc-220d7ac7d4d1&sectionRank=4', 'Legal Senior Officer', 'APL Tower - Central Park 28th Floor, Jl. S. Parman Kav. 28, Podomoro City Grogol, Petamburan, Jakarta Barat - 11470', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Melakukan review kontrak/perjanjian</li><li>Berkoordinasi dengan Bank atau Notaris untuk pelaksanaan pengajuan financing group perusahaan</li><li>Mempersiapkan dokumen RUPS dan koordinasi dengan Notaris untuk pembuatan akta terkait RUPS perusahaan</li><li>Melakukan pembaharuan perizinan (SIUP, TDP, Domisili atau perizinan OSS)</li><li>Berkoordinasi dengan holding perusahaan dalam kaitannya dengan group structuring</li></ul><div>Kualifikasi:</div><ul><li>Pendidikan min. S1 Hukum dengan IPK min. 3.00</li><li>Berpengalaman min. 3 tahun di bidang Corporate Legal</li><li>Menguasai komputer literasi dengan baik</li><li>Memiliki kemampuan analisa serta konseptual yang baik</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-10', '2020-09-10 21:16:34'),
(78, 60, 68, 3216, 32, 'research-development-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/research-and-development-manager-3349620?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=1', 'Research and Development Manager', 'Jl. Sulawesi blok M 27, Kawasan Cibitung MM2100, Cikarang Selatan, Bekasi, Jawa Barat, Indonesia', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div><strong>Jobs Description</strong></div><ol><li>Oversees the day-to-day activities in his/her department.</li><li>Coordinates with other interdepartmental Managers on all problems related to his/her area of responsibility.</li><li>Represents the company in interactions with the industry, supplier and service providers.</li><li>Reviews, finalize and signs all reports submitted to him/her by QA Manager, R&D Superior and subordinate staff.</li><li>Ensures that existing product identity is maintained for all products all the time through compliance and support of all SOPs, Guidelines and Standards.</li><li>Develops and implement programs to support  the objectives of the KPIs of her Departement.</li><li>Leads the implementation of internal programs like ISO, GMP, 5S and HACCP.</li><li>Enforces  disciplinary actions as maybe necessary to subordinate personnel in accordance with existing company policies and guidelines.</li><li>Participates in Profit Improvement Programs as directed by Marketing and/or management.</li><li>Participates in MANCOM meetings.</li><li>May do other tasks assigned to her by the General Manager</li></ol><div><strong>Qualifications</strong></div><ol><li>Educational Level – Must be a graduate of Food Technology, B.S. Chemistry, BS Chemical Engineering or any related Science/course ; preferably with MBA degree.</li><li>Experience-At least 8-12 years experience working in a food company with exposures to different food categories.</li><li>Communication Skills – High level of communication skills required to interface across all management levels and interdepartmental personnel.</li><li>Managerial Skills-Required to managing personnel from Section Manager 2 (M2) and down. Ability to plan, organize , lead and control work activities , projects, initiatives and other activities.</li><li>Language Skills-Ability to read, analyze, and interpret common scientific  and technical journals, financial reports, and legal documents. Ability to respond to common inquiriesor complaints from customers, regulatory agencies , or members of the business community.</li><li>Mathematical Skills- Ability to work with mathematical concepts such as proability and statistical inference.</li><li>Reasoning Ability-Ability to apply principles of logical or scientific thinking to a wide range of intellectual and practical problems. Ability to deal with nonverbal symbolism (formulas, scientific equations, graphs, musical notes, etc.) in its most difficult phases. Ability to deal with a variety of abstract and concrete variables.</li><li>Must be of good moral character.</li></ol></div></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 10:56:03'),
(79, 12, 69, 3216, 32, 'hrga-senior-staff', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/hrga-senior-staffteam-leader-3349618?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=2', 'HRGA Senior Staff / Team Leader', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya Gelar Sarjana di Manajemen HR, Psikologi, Hukum, Lainnya atau setara.</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 5 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang HRGA di perusahaan PMA Jepang</li><li>Memahami ilmu hukum perburuhan dan ilmu psikologi yang baik.</li><li>Memiliki sertifikat HRO dari BNSP.</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 10:58:24'),
(80, 48, 70, 1571, 15, 'marketing-representative-office', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/marketing-representative-office-jambi-3349617?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=3', 'Marketing Representative Office', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor\'s Degree in any field.</li><li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li><li>Required Skill(s): Communication Skill, Analystical Skill, Negotiation Skill,</li><li>Preferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor) specialized in Marketing/Business Development or equivalent.</li><li>Preferably from General Insurance Company, handling Leasing and Dealer.</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:01:11'),
(81, 24, 71, 3173, 31, 'it-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/it-manager-3349614?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=4', 'IT Manager', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div>Deskripsi pekerjaan:</div><ul><li>Memastikan semua sistem IT dapat berjalan dengan lancar</li><li>Memonitor pelaksanaan strategi dan kebijakan agar sesuai dengan kebijakan perusahaan</li><li>Menyediakan layanan dan pengembangan dalam lingkup IT dan komunikasi</li><li>Melakukan analisa, planning dan desain terhadap aplikasi dan sistem IT</li><li>Bertanggung jawab atas pengembangan dan peningkatan sistem IT</li><li>Melakukan analisis terhadap spesifikasi dan efektifitas aplikasi baru</li></ul><div>Kualifikasi:</div><ul><li>Pendidikan minimal S1 Ilmu Komputer</li><li>Memiliki pengalaman sebagai IT Manager minimal selama 5 tahun</li><li>Memiliki keahlian di Networking, Security and Infrastructure</li><li>Memiliki pengalaman membangun sistem ERP/SAP/HRIS, dan/atau sejenisnya</li><li>Penempatan: Slipi - Jakarta Barat</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:02:52'),
(82, 11, 72, 3515, 35, 'admin-lelang', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/admin-lelang-3349613?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=5', 'Admin Lelang', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya SMA di bidang apapun.</li><li>Fresh Graduate are welcome to apply, diutamakan yang berpengalaman dibidangnya</li><li>Kemampuan yang harus dimiliki: Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Power Point), komunikatif, bekerja dalam tim, adaptif terhadap setiap perubahan, bekerja dibawah tekanan</li><li>Lebih disukai Lulusan baru/Pengalaman kerja kurang dari 1 tahun khusus dalam Clerical/Staf Admin atau setara.</li></ul><div><strong>Deskripsi singkat pekerjaan:</strong></div><ul><li>Menyiapkan dokumen untuk lelang</li><li>Mencari informasi mengenai lelang dan tender yang akan diikuti</li><li>Membantu tim teknis dalam menyiapkan personil</li><li>Membuat Schedule kerja mandiri</li><li>Memantau lelang yang akan dimulai</li><li>Pekerjaan administrasi lainnya</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:05:21'),
(83, 16, 73, 3471, 34, 'graphic-designer', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/graphic-designer-3349611?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=6', 'Graphic Designer', 'Jl. Magelang No. 65, Kricak, Tegalrejo, Yogyakarta 55242', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div xss=removed><div>SoftwareSeni is a Software Development Company based in Yogyakarta & Australia. We love solving tough problems – from user experience to design and code. We build enterprise web-based solution for clients all over the world, from Australia, Indonesia, Europe, Africa and America.</div><div> </div><div>We are a growing business and need a Graphic Designer to accelerate that growth.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Where will you work?</strong><br> SoftwareSeni is nestled in amazing Yogyakarta. It\'s not just in any Yogyakarta, our office is right in the heart of Yogyakarta within walking distance from the famous Tugu Yogya. You can easily find a great place to dine nearby.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Who should apply?</strong><br> People who want to make a difference. People who want to be a part of team. People who are interested in building a company that’s bigger than the four walls of building. People who embody curiosity, awareness, resoluteness and emphaty – who are flexible, proactive, and driven.</div><div> </div></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><div><div><strong>Skills & Requirement</strong></div><ul><li xss=removed><strong>Basic HTML and CSS knowledge is a must.</strong></li><li xss=removed>Graphic and Layout Design</li><li xss=removed>Intermediate spoken and written English</li><li xss=removed>Web Design experience (UI/UX)</li><li xss=removed>Creative and innovative</li><li xss=removed>Good attitude</li></ul></div><div><strong>Responsibilities</strong></div><ul><li xss=removed>Create designs, concepts, and sample layouts based on knowledge of layout principles and esthetic design concepts.</li><li xss=removed>Determine size and arrangement of illustrative material and copy, and select style and size of type.</li><li xss=removed>Use computer software to generate new images.</li><li xss=removed>Mark up, paste, and assemble final layouts to prepare layouts for printer.</li><li xss=removed>Draw and print charts, graphs, illustrations, and other artwork, using computer.</li><li xss=removed>Review final layouts and suggest improvements as needed.</li></ul></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Compensation and Benefit :</strong></div><ul><li><strong>Health Insurance & Retirement Plan</strong>. We commited to pay 80% of your BPJS Kesehatan and 75% of your BPJS Ketenagakerjaan.</li><li><strong>Career Development & Training</strong>. We have a wonderful onboarding process where we help a new team member to get familiar with the way we work. There are training program devised that you get up to speed with the best practice we have here along with a pair partner review.</li><li><strong>Reasonable schedules</strong>. It’s sad that we even need to list this as a benefit. But we don’t stretch the team too thin. We only do “crunch times” in very rare occasion. We are encouraging culture where people can have a good work-life balance.</li><li><strong>Flexible Schedule</strong>. Our schedules are pretty flexible. Need to run an errand in the middle of the day? Totally cool. We have people who put in their eight hours in a row. Others who break it up throughout the day.</li><li><strong>English Class</strong>. We took our pride on our English class. Working in SoftwareSeni means that you would get massive improvement on your English, both spoken and written guarantee!</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:07:51'),
(84, 47, 74, 3671, 36, 'ecommerce-staff', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/ecommerce-staff-3349610?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=7', 'Ecommerce Staff', 'Green Lake City, Rukan Crown F no. 21D-E petir cipondoh kota tangerang', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div><strong>Persyaratan :</strong></div><ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya D3, S1 di Marketing,PR,Manajemen,Ilmu Komputer/Teknologi Informasi, Bisnis/Administrasi/Manajemen, Seni/Desain/Multimedia Kreatif atau setara.</li><li>Pengalaman 1-2 tahun di dunia marketing,terutama di dunia digital dan memiliki kemampuan client services</li><li>Paham dunia digital terutama marketing </li><li>Punya inisiatif tinggi dan selalu curious dengan hal baru</li><li>Cekatan dan terbiasa kerja rapih dan menggunakan data</li><li>Terbiasa analisa pasar marketplace</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Deskripsi pekerjaan:</strong></div><ul><li>Mengelola semua akun official di onlineshop / marketplace</li><li>Melakukan kerjasama dengan online marketplace untuk kegiatan marketing</li><li>Reporting database penjualan online</li><li>Melakukan CRM online (berhubungan dengan admin, database dan relationship), Checking Price Olshop</li><li>Terbiasa menangani client dan terbiasa dengan administrasi merketing.</li></ul></div><div> </div></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:10:26'),
(85, 51, 75, 3173, 31, 'sales-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/sales-manager-3349607?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=8', 'Sales Manager', 'Gedung Graha Kencana, Lt. 9 Unit G, Jl. Perjuangan Raya No. 88, Kebon Jeruk, Jakarta Barat, Special Capital Region of Jakarta, Indonesia - 11530', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div xss=removed>Strengthen and enlarge the market position of Shanghai Kaiquan Group in Indonesia.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Maximizing total sales by in coordinating and following the sales strategies set by the Indonesia Representative and Shanghai Head Quarter.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Job tasks in detail:</strong></div><ul><li xss=removed>Realization of the marketing and sales strategies.</li><li xss=removed>Reach sales targets by in charging a group of sales, making sure that their performance is up to the company requirement. </li><li xss=removed>Develop a sales team, guiding and supporting them towards efficient, target oriented and achieve their individual set sales target.</li><li xss=removed>Design, supervised, and evaluate the sales statistics as well as the KPI for all sales staff.</li><li xss=removed>In charge of certain market segments, to achieve own sales target.</li><li xss=removed>Sales, marketing and competition with relevant reporting.</li><li xss=removed>Sales promotion action for pumps and services as well as increasing Kaiquan Brand recognitions.</li><li xss=removed>Set up training plans for the Sales team.</li><li xss=removed>Increase the way, frequency and quality of communication with customers in all possible ways.</li><li xss=removed>Weekly and monthly reporting to Management regarding to daily sales activities and project information.</li><li xss=removed>focus on existing customer base as well as on developing new customers.</li><li xss=removed>Planning, organization and preparation of sales meetings and regular customers / distributors meetings.</li><li xss=removed>Involvement in the conception and organization of trade shows and sales conferences.</li><li xss=removed>Preparation, organization and realization of trainings, workshops and presentations at certain customers.</li><li xss=removed>Ensure handling and evaluation (technical and commercial clarification) of customer inquiries in best possible way and develop qualitative solutions.</li><li xss=removed>Ensure correct verification of customer orders in both technical aspects as well as commercial conditions.</li><li xss=removed>Constant working on correct attitude of sales staff during customer visits and following of company policies.</li><li xss=removed>Report directly to Indonesia’s office representative.</li><li xss=removed>To be placed in Surabaya and Sumatera Island.</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Requirements: </strong></div><ul><li xss=removed>Minimum Bachelor in engineering (mechanical or electrical); knowledge of business administration basics.</li><li xss=removed>Minimum 10 years working experience in the pumping industry); Proven record in sales management.</li><li xss=removed>Have relationship with the consultants, contractors or owner/end user are preferred.</li><li xss=removed>High knowledge of English language in spoken as well as writing.</li><li xss=removed>Have driving license and got own transportation.</li></ul></div><div> </div></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:12:41'),
(86, 46, 76, 3674, 36, 'digital-marketer-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/digital-marketing-manager-3349606?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=9', 'DIGITAL MARKETING MANAGER', 'Jl Raya Serpong KM 7, Komp Multi Guna Blok B.2 No.2, South Tangerang, Banten, Indonesia', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div xss=removed><strong>Anda senang membangun brand? Berjiwa kreatif dan mengerti social media/websites? Suka dengan dunia fashion?</strong></div><div xss=removed>Jadilah <strong>DIGITAL MARKETING MANAGER</strong> di Vigindo Group hanya jika Anda:</div><ol><li xss=removed>Senang membangun brand dan sadar dengan kekuatan social media advertising</li><li xss=removed>Memiliki kepercayaan diri yang tinggi dan berpenampilan menarik</li><li xss=removed>Nyaman bertemu dengan orang baru untuk menjalin kerja sama</li><li xss=removed>Mengerti kekuatan digital marketing secara keseluruhan</li></ol><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Vigindo Group</strong> adalah perusahaan  yang berdiri sejak tahun 1998, dengan focus pada bidang fashionpria . Saat ini, produk kami tersedia secara luas di department store ternama di Indonesia.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><ul><li xss=removed>Posisi <strong>DIGITAL MARKETING</strong>  ini bertanggungjawab terhadap pengembangan lini bisnis Vigindo Group  secara digital (on-line) dan memperkuat posisi Vigindo Group secara off-line.</li><li xss=removed>Mengelola dan memaksimalkan social media seperti Facebook, Instagram dll  untuk meningkatkan penjualan.</li><li xss=removed>Mengelola dan memaksimalkan penjualan secara on-line di market place yang sesuai dengan target market Vigindo.</li><li xss=removed>Menjalin hubungan dengan institusi / organisasi lain yang tepat untuk menciptakan kerja sama dan strategi aliansi yang bisa mendatangkan banyak calon pelanggan.</li><li xss=removed>Mengkoordinasikan acara-acara yang dapat mendatangkan banyak calon pelanggan.</li><li xss=removed>Merancang strategi marketing digital yang terpadu dan berkesinambungan untuk bisa mendatangkan banyak pelanggan.</li><li xss=removed>Sebagai Brand Guardian pada setiap iklan marketing yang dikomunikasikan.</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Requirements:</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><ol><li xss=removed>Minimal S1, jurusan Marketing Management, Public Relations, Communications, Desain Komunikasi Visual.</li><li xss=removed>Minimal 3 tahun pengalaman di Digital Marketing Management atau Marketing Manager</li><li xss=removed>Mahir dalam penggunaan social media dan paham copy writing.</li><li xss=removed>Dapat menggunakan Microsoft Office</li><li xss=removed><strong>Diutamakan</strong> yang juga mahir dalam photography, penggunaan program yang diperlukan dalam proses design, seperti Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator,Corel Draw, Adobe Premiere termasuk video editing software.</li><li xss=removed>Memiliki kepribadian menyenangkan, senang bersosialisasi, berpikir kritis, percaya diri, dewasa dan memiliki jiwa melayani.</li></ol><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Benefits:</strong></div><ul><li xss=removed>Quarterly Incentive : Berdasarkan Kinerja Pribadi</li><li xss=removed>Annual Bonus : Berdasarkan Kinerja Perusahaan dan Pribadi</li><li xss=removed>Full Employment : Status Kepegawaian Tetap</li><li xss=removed>Allowances : Tunjangan Kesehatan dan Tunjuangan Pensiun</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Hanya jika Anda memenuhi kriteria, ACTION sekarang juga!</strong></div><div xss=removed><strong>Kirim Resume + Photo + Gaji Terakhir Anda </strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>All resumes will be handled strictly confidential and only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</div></div></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:15:12'),
(87, 9, 77, 3578, 35, 'admin-billing', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/admin-billing-3349605?fr=J&searchRequestToken=35565100-4222-4f37-c803-02e88ef818d5&sectionRank=10', 'Admin Billing', '25 Raya Kedung Baruk, Surabaya, East Java, Indonesia', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Kandidat harus memiliki setidaknya Diploma di Ekonomi, Keuangan/Akuntansi/Perbankan atau setara.</li><li>Diutamakan S1 jurusan Akuntansi</li><li>Setidaknya memiliki 1 tahun pengalaman dalam bidang yang sesuai untuk posisi ini.</li><li>Lebih disukai Lulusan baru/Pengalaman kerja kurang dari 1 tahun khusus dalam Keuangan - Keuangan Perusahaan/Investasi/Perbankan Retail atau setara.</li><li>Berdomisili di Balikpapan (Batakan)</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-11', '2020-09-11 11:17:52'),
(88, 11, 78, 1207, 12, 'admin-purchasing', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/adm-purchasing-3350112?fr=J&src=16&searchRequestToken=262e4b65-3f3e-499b-b856-25a5f6d7b062&sectionRank=81', 'Adm. Purchasing', 'JL Pertahanan No 17 Patumbak-Deli Serdang- SUMUT', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div><strong>Requirements:</strong></div><ul><li>Minimal lulusan D3 semua jurusan</li><li>Pengalaman kerja minimal 3 tahun di bagian Administrasi</li><li>Ketelitian dan tanggung jawab sangat diutamakan</li><li>Menguasai design (Corel Draw, Photoshop) merupakan nilai tambah</li><li>Mampu mengoperasikan komputer dengan sangat baik (Ms. Excel, Word)</li><li>Rapi, bersih, mau belajar, rajin dan cekatan.</li><li>Bisa bekerja dalam satu tim</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Job Description:</strong></div><ul><li>Verifikasi design artwork dari supplier kemasan dibandingkan dengan permintaan customer.</li><li>Menerbitkan Purchase Order yang sesuai permintaan pelanggan.</li><li>Merekap data-data yang diperlukan untuk keperluan Purchasing.</li><li>Follow up barang masuk dari supplier sesuai jadwal yang sudah ditentukan.</li><li>Memastikan barang yang diorder telah diterima tepat waktu dan quantity sesuai.</li></ul></div></div>', 1, '2020-10-12', '2020-09-12 21:47:27'),
(89, 41, 79, 3204, 32, 'general-manager', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/general-manager-3350111?fr=J&src=16&searchRequestToken=262e4b65-3f3e-499b-b856-25a5f6d7b062&sectionRank=82', 'General Manager', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Perhatian General Manager yang Mempunyai Pengalaman Minimal 10 Tahun di Industri Manufaktur</strong></div><div> </div><div><strong>Kami adalah PT Bakerindo Mitra Perkasa </strong>yang memiliki visi menjadi perusahaan manufaktur oven bakery terdepan di Indonesia mencari orang yang luar biasa untuk bergabung dan membangun perusahaan ini.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Jadilah General Manager kami jika Anda</strong>:</div><ul><li>Memiliki minimal 10 tahun pengalaman dalam industri manufaktur dan minimal 5 tahun pengalaman memegang jabatan manajemen.</li><li>Memiliki setidaknya Gelar Sarjana di bidang yang sesuai dengan posisi ini.</li><li>Memiliki keahlian/pengetahuan: <ul><li><strong>Manajemen keuangan: </strong>Mampu membaca dan menganalisa laporan keuangan perusahaan.</li><li><strong>Manajemen SDM: </strong><ul><li><strong>?</strong>Mampu menganalisa kebutuhan SDM dalam perusahaan.</li><li>Mampu mengatur dan memotivasi bawahan.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Manajemen kendali mutu (QC): </strong>Mampu menerapkan konsep kendali mutu atau QC dalam setiap proses, dari penerimaan bahan baku sampai pengiriman barang jadi.</li><li><strong>Fabrikasi lembaran logam (sheet metal): </strong>Mengusai teknik-teknik fabrikasi lembaran logam seperti bending, laser cutting, assembling & finishing.</li></ul></li><li>Nilai plus jika menguasai: <ul><li>Desain sistem termal (Thermal System Design).</li><li>Konsep 5S atau 5R.</li><li>Software 3D CAD.</li></ul></li></ul><div><strong>Hanya jika memenuhi kriteria</strong>, kirimkan CV Anda lewat Jobstreet.co.id paling lambat tanggal 22 September 2020.</div></div>', 1, '2020-10-12', '2020-09-12 21:49:42'),
