(136, 8, 112, 3201, 32, 'field-account-consultant', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/karya-bakti-bca-finance-field-account-consultant-bogor-3351168?fr=J&searchRequestToken=3aea908e-b138-4cd7-85b7-01748bbebf84&sectionRank=7', 'Karya Bakti BCA Finance - Field Account Consultant Bogor', 'Bogor', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><div>Program Karya Bakti BCA Finance Merupakan program kerja dari PT. BCA Finance dimana karyawan mendapatkan uang penghargaan total sebesar 38 Juta selama program berlangsung diluar benefit lainnya.</div><div> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Gambaran Pekerjaan :</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Mengingatkan, melakukan observasi, analisa, dan penagihan melalui telepon ataupun kunjungan langsung kepada konsumen yang pembayarannya melebihi tanggal jatuh tempo dengan tetap menjaga hubungan baik dengan konsumen.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div><strong>Persyaratan :</strong></div><ul><li>Pendidikan D3/S1 minimal IPK 2,5 atau SMU dengan NEM rata-rata 6,5.</li><li>Usia maksimal 24 tahun untuk fresh graduated D3/S1 dan maksimal usia 20 tahun untuk pendidikan SMU.</li><li>Wajib memiliki SIM C dan sepeda motor.</li><li>Domisili Bogor dan sekitarnya.</li><li>Penempatan di Cabang BCA Finance Bogor</li></ul></div><div> </div></div>', 1, '2020-10-15', '2020-09-15 08:35:26'),
(137, 32, 113, 3513, 35, 'techician-garage', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/technician-garage-and-heavy-equipment-3351166?fr=J&searchRequestToken=3aea908e-b138-4cd7-85b7-01748bbebf84&sectionRank=8', 'Technician Garage and Heavy Equipment', 'PT. Paiton Operation & Maintenance Indonesia Jl. Raya Surabaya - Situbondo Km. 141 Paiton 67291 Probolinggo, Jawa Timur.', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></div><ul><li>Heavy Equipment Maintenance Management : HE Availability & Reliability, Implement the heavy equipment maintenance programs, in the meanwhile, determine engine life cycle and record service history, the engine maintenance management, determine level engine parts, control contaminant, SOS oil analysis, reduce fuel cost, the maintenance management programs, maintenance records, apply effective engine maintenance management, implement 7 elements of the maintenance planning, determine the claim, Review mobile equipment problems, improve the equipment performance and determine impact operations and the operating procedures, priorities maintenance orders to maintain reliability and availability of the mobile equipment</li><li>The Heavy Equipment / Light Vehicle Routine check activity: Inspection & Test, Motivate, review and supervise performance of mobile equipment including light vehicles and diesel engine generator set, Check and clean up undercarriage of heavy equipment as the manual schedule.</li><li>Planning & Scheduling : Implement the  planning  and scheduling of all Heavy Equipment and Light Vehicle preventive maintenance and mid- and long-term maintenance and repair projects, Priorities on the basis of general work schedules, methods and policies established by higher levels of supervision, Implement  scheduling of repair and maintenance work on equipment with other HE / LV Contractor</li><li>The Garage and Workshop Management : Direct, plan and control the Heavy Equipment workshop, preparation, tools and consumables arrangement, to achieve the good condition and long lifetime of all the mobile system, Maintain availability of spare parts (fast moving part, consumable part, oil etc.)</li><li>Dealers, Suppliers, Vendors Communication & Supervision: Supervision with Heavy Equipment / Light Vehicle contractors on warranty and maintenance / modification work, Co-ordinate with dealers, vendors and suppliers to maintain the good condition of all the equipment</li></ul><div><strong>General Requirements:</strong></div><ul><li>The candidate should have Engineering Technical Diploma (D-3) preferable mechanic</li><li>3 years working experience in a large modern Power Station or similar industry</li><li>Have good oral and written English communication skills.</li><li>A good working knowledge of power station plant, maintenance shutdown etc.</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-15', '2020-09-15 08:37:37'),
(138, 47, 114, 3174, 31, 'admin-marketing-online', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/admin-marketing-online-3351165?fr=J&searchRequestToken=3aea908e-b138-4cd7-85b7-01748bbebf84&sectionRank=9', 'Admin Marketing Online', '', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Job Description:</strong><br> ?Membuat laporan penjualan secara periodik/berkala<br> ? Menjawab semua pertanyaan/komentar/keluhan yang datang dari para pengguna aplikasi<br> ?Memastikan proses penjualan online berjalan dengan lancar, termasuk didalamnya memenuhi target penjualan yang ditetapkan perusahaan.<br> ?Bertanggung jawab atas semua hal yang berhubungan dengan pemasaran dan branding secara digital.<br> ?Menyusun perencanaan untuk promosi melalui channel digital berbentuk Social Media, Content Marketing, Email Marketing, Video Marketing, dll<br> ?Membuat konsep dan merancang distribusi content campaign marketing di media sosial.<br> ?Memelihara dan meningkatkan engagement pengguna applikasi melalui penyampaian content di media sosial.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Skills:</strong><br> ?Pengalaman kerja min 1 tahun</div><div>?Pendidikan minimal D3<br> ?Usia 20 – 35 tahun<br> ?Kemampuan riset pasar dan berpikir strategis<br> ?Keterampilan dalam berkomunikasi<br> ?Familiar alur penjualan marketplace online<br> ?Dapat mengoperasikan Ms. Word & Ms. Excel<br> ?Menguasai tata kelola administrasi dan pelaporan</div></div>', 1, '2020-10-15', '2020-09-15 08:40:04'),
(139, 70, 115, 3174, 31, 'office-assistant', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/office-assistant-3350517?fr=J&searchRequestToken=3aea908e-b138-4cd7-85b7-01748bbebf84&sectionRank=10', 'Office Assistant', 'Plaza Karinda Blok B1 No 17, Jl Karang Tengah Raya, Lebak Bulus - Jakarta Selatan', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <ul><li>Pendidikan min SMA/Sederajat</li><li>Pengalaman sebagai Office Assistant min 2 tahun</li><li>Paham dengan alat kebersihan</li><li>Paham menggunakan mesin fotokopi dan alat elektronik kantor</li><li>Memiliki komunikasi yang baik</li><li>Penampilan menarik</li></ul></div>', 1, '2020-10-15', '2020-09-15 08:41:58');
