(5, 1, 'PT Prasada Daya Utama INNERTRUE', 'pt-prasada-daya-utama-innertrue', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/162758/images/logo/162758_logo_0_604173.jpg', '', NULL, 'Smart Casual', 'Indonesia & Inggris', '-', 'Senin-Jumat', '1-50 Pekerja', '<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=\"removed\">Prasada Daya Utama is\r\nbrand new company and part of a large company group which is the leader in the the Retail and Music\r\nindustry since 1987. To expand the wings, the company has decided to enter the Beauty & Wellness\r\nIndustry with \'INNERTRUE\' being their first beauty brand. INNERTRUE is a modern adaptive\r\nskincare made locally in Indonesia with a global vision, utilizing the latest technology, innovation and\r\nInternational award winning ingredients.</div> <div xss=\"removed\"> </div> <div xss=\"removed\">The focus of the brand is to bring out the best of nature and the true beauty of\r\nhuman beings as the way to achieve balance and true happiness. </div><p></p>', 'INNERTRUE is a young and dynamic company that allows the team members to learn, experience, grow and optimise their true potentials while contributing positive changes to society through their contributions in the company.'),
(6, 7, 'Innovative Community Center', 'innovative-community-center', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/247969/images/logo/247969_logo_0_957859.jpg', '', NULL, 'Formal (contoh: Kemeja - Dasi)', 'Indonesia', '-', 'Reguler. Senin-Jumat', '1-50 Pekerja', '<p>Innovative Community Center yang beralamat di Semarang, merupakan perusahaan yang bergerak dalam bidang IT & Telecommunication. Demi kemajuan perusahaan kami mengedepankan visi dan misi, adapun kebiasaan yang kami lakukan di perusahaan kami yaitu secara terus menerus akan melakukan perbaikan dan menciptakan ide-ide terbaru dalam proses bisnis kami. Tentunya dengan pelayanan oleh tenaga profesional kami selalu memberikan solusi dan kontribusi dengan kenyaman dan kepuasan customer, kami sangat berpengalaman dibidangnya karena sudah menjalani masa training secara visi dan misi perusahaan kedepan untuk lebih baik.<br></p>', ''),
(7, 2, 'PT Supravisi Rama Optik Manufacturing', 'pt-supravisi-rama-optik-manufacturing', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/14039/images/logo/14039_logo_0.jpg', '', NULL, 'Bussiness - Uniform', 'Indonesia - Inggris', 'Kesehatan', 'Reguler, Senin-Jum\'at', '200 - 500 Pekerja', 'With more than 30 years of experience in tinting lenses, it is no wonder we can produce the most exhilarating customized colours. For great accessories and to add an edge to your fashion statement, you can use our Fashion Tint Lens and select from our extensive colour collections. It is a great fit either to be used for day and night.', '<div xss=removed>As a rapidly growing company, We have a corporate culture that is dynamic,\r\ncreative, and innovative as well as providing an opportunity for you to develop a career with us. We are\r\nseeking for highly motivated, dynamic, creative and disciplined willing to come forward and join us and be\r\none of our great team.</div>\r\n'),
(8, 2, 'RGF HR Agent Indonesia', 'rgf-hr-agent-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/40909/images/logo/40909_logo_0_393009.jpeg', 'https://www.rgf-hragent.asia/en/indonesia', NULL, '', '', '', '', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '', ''),
(9, 8, 'PT Osa Putra Engineering', 'pt-osa-putra-engineering', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/194699/images/logo/194699_logo_0_476996.jpg', '', NULL, 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', '', 'Reguler, Senin-Jum\'at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<strong>PT. Osa Putra Engineering  </strong>is  a professional company specialized in all sorts of  liquid and semisolid products that integrated with all factory production  facilities including engineering,manufacturing,automation    programming,   installation,  commissioning and services that turn out into solution  provider for manufacturing  company.\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since its founding  in 2011, our company gradually has been growing into a  bigger as manufacturer  in processing equipment  and plant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gathering various  engineering  background  with abundant experiences in that industry,  we strive  our  best to deliver high quality, reliable products, and problem solving for <strong>Pharmaceutical,Cosmetic, </strong><strong>Food, Dairy, Beverage and Chemical  Industry </strong>to support our customers in order to their  production  activity  will be optimum  and efficient.</p>\r\n\r\n<p> </p>\r\nThe equipment  ranges from compact module to fully integrated factory production facilities, all featuring  modular designed equipment.  Osa has many standard models and they are designed to meet customers requirements.', ''),
(10, 8, 'PT Java Seafood', 'pt-java-seafood', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/53855/images/logo/53855_logo_0_39072.jpg', 'http://www.java-seafood.com/', NULL, 'Kasual', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, BPJS Ketenaga Kerjaan', 'Senin - Sabtu', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<p></p><div xss=removed>The mother company,\r\nLF Food is the subsidiary company of the biggest fashion and food business group in Korea that established\r\nPT Java Seafood (JVS) in Indonesia.<br> It was incorporated in July 2011 and started production from July\r\n2014 and it is one of the largest surimi plant which as 8,000 MT production capacity in Indonesia.<br> It is\r\nemployed by 250 workers including Thai and Korean professional technicians to produce premium surimi\r\nwith Indonesia natural heritage and resources.<br> JVS\'s competitive advantage is due to the\r\nstrategic location which is surrounded plenty and short-distanced by fishing ports. It reduces</div><p></p>', '<div xss=removed>As shareholder of Lucky Union Food Co., Ltd.<br> in Thailand, the\r\npremium surimi seafood producers in the world,<br> JVS is designed to be driven towards consumers\r\nrequirement.<br> JVS has international required quality assurance programs including the proper water and\r\ntemperature adjustment also hygiene and sanitary regulation to meet adequate quality standard.</div>'),
(11, 8, 'PT Hwa Seung Indonesia', 'pt-hwa-seung-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/67463/images/logo/67463_logo_0_484986.png', 'http://www.inforekruthwi.online/', NULL, 'Uniform', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Senin - Jum\'at :  07:00 - 16:00', 'Lebih dari 5000 Pekerja', '<strong>PENGUMUMAN :</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><strong>Kami tidak memungut biaya apapun dalam proses rekrutmen</strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Kami tidak pernah bekerja sama dengan travel agent / biro perjalanan tertentu dalam proses rekrutmen.</strong></li>\r\n <li><strong>Apabila Anda diminta untuk membayar sejumlah uang dalam bentuk pembayaran tiket pesawat dan hotel atau akomodasi lainnya agar diabaikan.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', '<ul> <li>Kami tidak memungut biaya apapun dalam proses rekrutmen</li> <li>Kami memberikan\r\ntunjangan transport, tunjangan kehadiran dan fasilitas makan siang.</li> <li>Tidak ada status karyawan\r\nkontrak (pengangkatan karyawan tetap setelah lolos evaluasi 3 bulan masa percobaan).</li> <li>Perusahaan\r\nini mendukung lingkungan kerja yang menyenangkan.</li> <li>Kami memiliki budaya komunikasi terbuka\r\nuntuk memberikan semangat komunikasi antar level.<br>  </li> </ul>\r\n'),
(12, 8, 'HOLI GROUP', 'holi-group', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/22129/images/logo/22129_logo_0_890504.jpg', 'http://holikaryasakti.com/', NULL, 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Inggris - Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lainnya', 'Monday - Friday', '1000 - 2000 Pekerja', '<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Holi Group\r\n adalah group perusahaan yang bergerak dalam beberapa bidang usaha dengan tujuan market baik \r\nlokal maupun eksport ke beberapa negara bagian Eropa, Japan, China, USA, dll. PT. Holi Karya Sakti\r\nberdiri sejak tahun 1989,  dan berlokasi di Grobogan – Jawa Tengah sebagai perusahaan\r\nutama. Beberapa bidang usaha yang kami kembangkan diantaranya :</div><div xss=removed> - Manufacturer dan Exporter Sports Gloves Product untuk Gloves meliputi :<br>\r\n        • SKI / Snowboard, Winter, Casual, Mountain\r\nClimbing, Driving, Cycling<br>         • Golf,Horse\r\nRiding Gloves,Shooting Gloves,Multifunction Gloves<br>\r\n        • dll</div><div xss=removed> -\r\nProcessing dan Eksporter Seafood Product untuk  brand fisher meliputi :<br>\r\n        • Frozen Demersal Fish<br>\r\n        • Frozen Shrimp<br>\r\n        • Frozen Surimi<br>\r\n        • dan lainnya</div><div xss=removed> - Production dan Distributor Plastic</div><div xss=removed> -\r\nEmbroidery<span xss=removed> </span></div> <div xss=removed>-dan\r\nlainnya</div> <p></p>', '<div xss=removed>Holi  Group dengan pengalaman lebih dari 30 tahun mampu\r\nmenunjukan eksistensi kepada consumer melalui beberapa item produk dan  dengan  jangkauan\r\nmarket hingga pasar international. Dengan bidang usaha yang tersebar pada beberapa cabang perusahaan,\r\nakan membuka kesempatan kerja yang semakin luas untuk dapat ditempatkan di salah satu branch group\r\nkami.</div> <div xss=removed><br> Hingga saat ini, PT. Holi Karya Sakti Group berkembang\r\ndengan lebih dari 1500 karyawan multiskill dan profesional. Sebagai usaha mempertahankan dan\r\nmengembangkan skill kinerja karyawan, kami selalu melakukan evaluasi, training dan konsep kerja yang\r\nnyaman sehingga dapat tercipta progres kerja baik secara individu maupun kearah team work.</div>'),
(13, 2, 'PT Raja Besi Semarang', 'pt-raja-besi-semarang', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/53756/images/logo/53756_logo_0_98324.png', 'http://rajabesi.co.id/', NULL, 'Uniform', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Monday - Saturday', '1000 - 2000 Pekerja', 'P.T. Raja Besi was a company in Semarang, Indonesia. With more than 30 years of experience in the steel sector, Raja Besi has become one of the leading private steel producers in the country. Its main products are Steel Pipes and CRC, although it also produces a range of other products witch includes C/ Lip Channels, Slotted Angle Channels, and CR/HR Steel Sheets. Raja Besi’s steel pipe products consists of Carbon Steel Pipes, Galvanized Steel Pipes, Furniture Pipes, Square Galvanized, Spiral Pipes, Conduit Steel Pipes, and Electric/Telephone/Street Lighting Steel Poles. With the help of 1200 skilled workers, Raja Besi’s production capacity reaches 200,000 MT annually.\r\n\r\n<p>Being located in Central Java also gives Raja Besi a competitive edge over its competitors. It allows Raja Besi to distribute its products in the island of Java more efficiently, encompassing the surrounding cities in Central Java, and the cities in the West and East Java. Thus, given all these advantage, Raja Besi is prepared to face the future with confidence.</p>', 'Bergabunglah dengan kami!'),
(14, 9, 'PT Smartfren Telecom Tbk', 'pt-smartfren-telecom-tbk', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/167/images/logo/167_logo_0_184396.jpg', 'http://www.smartfren.com/', NULL, 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia & Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan Lain, Gigi, Olahraga, Parkir', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '2000 - 5000 Pekerja', '<p></p><div xss=\"removed\"><strong>SMARTFREN\r\nTelecom, part of Sinar Mas group,</strong> is one of the fastest growing telecommunication provider in\r\nIndonesia. The company main business is internet service provider and cellular operator. Starting 2015,\r\nSmartfren has established 4G LTE technology, committed to give wider, faster and more stable 4G\r\nexperience</div><p></p>\r\n', '<div xss=\"removed\">We take pride in our strong team culture - one of mutual trust, learning,\r\nsharing, care, willingness, cooperation and concern. This includes providing a conducive, family-friendly\r\nwork environment that enhances our staff\'s professional and personal growth. We are seeking for\r\nhighly motivated, dynamic, independent individuals and disciplined person who willing to come forward\r\nand can work independently and team work and be one of our great team.</div>'),
(15, 9, 'PT Mitra Prodin', 'pt-mitra-prodin', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/47388/images/logo/47388_logo_0_598402.jpg', 'https://mitraprodin.com/', NULL, 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia & Inggris', 'Kesehatan, BPJS Kesehatan, BPjS Ketenagakerjaan, In-house clinic', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '2000 - 5000 Pekerja', '<p>PT. Mitra Prodin, manufacturer of high quality, hand-rolled cones and designer & producer of innovative cone filling devices, is substantially expanding its facilities and workforce of already 2500 workers. Our head office is located at JL. Prof. I.B. Mantra, Kesiman Kertalangu, Denpasar Timur, Bali.</p>', '<p>PT Mitra Prodin is a fast paced company where suitable candidates can work & grow. We strongly believe in taking care of the well-being of our employees. Beside the law-required benefits, we also provide daily Zumba and weekly laughing Yoga classes.</p>\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n<p>Employees who have worked for 3 years will be automatically offered a permanent contract with additional benefits such as a company pension plan.</p>'),
(16, 10, 'CV Prima Utama', 'cv-prima-utama', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/153566/images/logo/153566_logo_0_751690.jpg', '', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Parkir', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<p>Perusahaan kami bergerak dalam bidang Tax Consultancy, Accounting Service Report, Tax Review, Tax Planning hingga Tax Audit.</p>', ''),
(17, 11, 'PT Finansia Multi Finance', 'pt-finansia-multi-finance', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/1595/images/logo/1595_logo_0.jpg', 'https://www.kreditplus.com', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Pinjama, Gigi, Parkir, Penglihatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', 'Lebih dari 5000 Pekerja', '<p>PT Finansia Multi Finance (“FMF” or “the Company”) was founded in 1994. FMF received its multifinance licence in 1994 and is fully licenced to conduct a full range of multifinance activities including consumer finance, leasing, factoring and credit cards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, FMF and its kreditplus brand are established as leading players within the multifinance sector with a focus on the used motorcycle financing, used car financing and white goods financing segments. As at 30 June 2014, FMF finances 772,234 customers through a proprietary distribution network of 313 branches / POS outlets and supported by a workforce of 13,682 employees.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>On its establishment, FMF adopted a dual focus on both the retail and commercial segment largely in response to the opportunities available in the market. Following the Asian Financial Crisis (“AFC”), FMF, like many other financial institutions in Indonesia, adjusted its strategic business model and risk management framework to reflect lessons learnt over the period.</p>\r\n<p>Over its 20 years of operation, FMF has weathered the course of a number of credit cycles and financial crises through a willingness and flexibility to adapt its business model and practices in response to shifting regulatory and operating environments. This adaptability has provided FMF with valuable operating experience within a number of different business segments and product groups across both the retail and commercial markets. </p>', '<p>A Leading Provider of Consumer Financing Products and Services In Indonesia</p>\r\n<p><b>A Leading Provider</b> means :</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the goal of Finansia to become a major player in Indonesia for consumer financing in the middle to low income segment. Management goal is to make this company to become number 1 in the business that we choose.</p>\r\n<b>Consumer Financing Products and Services</b> means :<p></p>\r\n<p>Finansia is focusing in Consumer financing business, with a portfolio consisting of motorcycles, automobiles and white goods financing.</p>\r\n<p><b>MISSION</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>To provide the best consumer financing products and services to the community.</li>\r\n <li>To establish a framework for people to learn, to develop and to perform, creating value and opportunities.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(18, 11, 'PT Alfa Valves Indonesia', 'pt-alfa-valves-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/39546/images/logo/39546_logo_0.jpg', 'http://www.alfa-valves.com/', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p>PT. ALFA VALVES INDONESIA is a domestic investment company with core business on Manufacturing and Services of Industrial Valves. We are looking for top talents who are ready to cross all frontier. Make the strategic move, join our team and catch the chance to follow your best career.</p>\r\n<p>PT. ALFA VALVES INDONESIA adalah sebuah perusahaan yang bergerak dibidang manufacture dengan product Valve. PT Alfa Valves Indonesia memproduksi berbagai macam valve sesuai dengan permintaan pasar. Product PT. Alfa Valves Indonesia banyak digunakan untuk Industri.</p>', '<p>We take pride in our strong team culture - one of mutual trust, learning, sharing, care, willingness, cooperation and concern. This includes providing a conducive, family-friendly work environment that enhances our staff\'s professional and personal growth. We are seeking for highly motivated, dynamic, independent individuals and disciplined person who willing to come forward and can work independently and team work and be one of our great team.</p>'),
(19, 11, 'PT Jessindo Prakarsa', 'pt-jessindo-prakarsa', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/62645/images/logo/62645_logo_0_770737.jpg', '', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Bonus tahunan', 'Regular hours, Monday - Saturday', '1000 - 2000 Pekerja', '<p>PT. Jessindo Prakarsa is a Distributor Company engaged in the distribution of Consumer Goods which has branches in several cities such as: Bogor, Sukabumi, Bekasi, Karawang, Purwakarta, Tangerang and Serang.</p>', '<p>Kami menawarkan peluang kerja dan kesempatan berkarir yang sama untuk semua level jabatan, suasana kerja yang kondusif dan transparan, serta target kerja yang membuat Anda bisa memberikan kemampuan maksimal bagi perkembangan perusahaan. Kami juga memberikan kesempatan bagi setiap karyawan untuk meningkatkan kapasitas pribadinya sehingga mampu menjadi pengelola dan pemilik dari sebuah unit usaha secara mandiri.</p>'),
(20, 12, 'MODENA INDONESIA', 'modena-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/1321/images/logo/1321_logo_0_33868.jpg', 'http://www.modena.com/', NULL, 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan Lainnya, Bantuan Pendidikan, Pinjaman, Gigi, Penglihatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<p>Since its inception in 1981, MODENA has become a trusted home appliances provider that markets 3 major product lines – cooking, cooling and cleaning, with a distinctive Italian design elegance. Not only to present high quality and realiable appliances, MODENA also implements Quality Management System ISO 9001 – 2008, and provides a fleet of competent call center agents as frontliners and service centers spread in tens of cities all over the country to ensure customer’s satisfaction and loyalty in the after sales service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MODENA has grown to be a market leader in the industry which is marked with a series of accolades that reflect company’s outstanding achievements. In 2010 and 2011 MODENA was recognized as number one brand most widely purchased in Indonesia for freestanding cooker, built-in hob, built-in oven and exhaust hood product categories, and has acquired over half of national market share. Reseached on customer’s satisfaction toward cooker/stove in the country conducted by MARS, has awarded MODENA with 5 Stars Quality Global Customer Satisfaction Standard (GCSS), which includes highest customer satisfaction index on customer expectation, customer loyalty, perceived quality and perceived value.For further information please visit www.modena.co.id.</p>', '<p><b>Our Vision</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\nTo be the preferred provider of home appliances for every household in the target market segment, and to be known by the consumers as a brand that delivers best quality products with service excellence.</p>\r\n<p><b>Our Mission</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>Provide customers a quality product.</li>\r\n <li>Provide added value to the stakeholders and community.</li>\r\n <li>Being a business partner choice.</li>\r\n <li>Being an employer of choice for the best human resources.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(21, 12, 'PT NIDHI KHANDA PRIMA', 'pt-nidhi-khanda-prima', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/214902/images/logo/214902_logo_0_936964.jpg', 'https://kontakk.com/@GYKACO', NULL, 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', '', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', 'Tidak spesifik', '<p>PT. NIDHI KHANDA PRIMA berdiri sejak tahun 1982, perusahaan ini bergerak di bidang<b> Trading Tas & Aksesoris Tas</b></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gykaco Tas (Shopee) - https://shopee.co.id/gykacobags</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gykaco Tas (Tokopedia) - https://www.tokopedia.com/gykaco?source=universe&st=product</p>', ''),
(22, 12, 'PT VERITAS SUKSES NUSANTARA', 'pt-veritas-sukses-nusantara', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/185746/images/logo/185746_logo_0_916364.jpg', '', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Intensif', 'Sabtu atau memerlukan shift', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<p>Dengan\r\nberkembang pesatnya Teknologi Informasi dalam dunia bisnis, kami mengundang individu - individu yang\r\nberkualitas untuk dapat bergabung dan maju bersama perusahaan kami.</p>\r\n', '<p>Kami percaya bahwa karyawan\r\nadalah aset berharga kami dan bahwa setiap orang di perusahaan kami adalah pemain kunci dalam\r\nmembantu perusahaan untuk mencapai puncak kesuksesan. Kami mencari professional yang termotivasi,\r\ndinamis, bertanggung jawab dan disiplin bersedia untuk maju dan bergabung dengan kami dan menjadi salah\r\nsatu tim hebat kami.</p>'),
(23, 12, 'Agung Sedayu Group', 'agung-sedayu-group', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/522/images/logo/522_logo_0_986356.jpg', 'http://www.agungsedayu.com/', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan Lainnya, Pinjaman, Gigi, Parkir, Marriage, Child Birth', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', 'Lebih dari 5000 Pekerja', '<p><b>With more than 41 years of experience,\r\nAgung Sedayu Group has established a remarkable track record of having developed qualified and great\r\ninvestment properties in Indonesia. </b></p><div xss=removed><b>  </b></div><b> <div xss=removed> <strong>Agung Sedayu Group is consistently recognized among the best\r\ncompanies to work for. We offer challenging career development, good working environment, competitive\r\nremuneration package, benefits, and trainings that enhance our professionals to keep growing. If you are a\r\ncommitted, talented, and competent professional, join us, in Agung Sedayu Group, to develop our\r\ncities.</strong></div> <div xss=removed>  </div> </b><div xss=removed><b>\r\n<strong>Join us in one diverse group of professionals, to develop remarkable projects and proud to\r\ncontribute in shaping our cities.</strong></b><strong> </strong></div>', '<p><b>Vision :</b></p>\r\n<p>Kami adalah property developer yang terpercaya dan menjadi market leader</p>\r\n<p><b>Mission</b> :</p>\r\n<p>Kami bertekad menjadi Property Developer yang selalu melayani dengan : Mutu Unggul, Tepat Waktu, dan Biaya Efisien</p>\r\n<p>CULTURE & VALUES :</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li><b>Credibility</b></li>\r\n <li>Berorientasi kepada profit melalui performance perusahaan yang dipercaya dan dihargai masyarakat </li>\r\n <li><strong><strong>• </strong>Professional</strong></li>\r\n <li>Berkemampuan tinggi dalam menjalankan tugas dan kewajiban serta efektif & efisien dalam bekerja</li>\r\n <li><b>Integrity</b></li>\r\n <li>Konsisten untuk berkarakter baik, bertanggung jawab, jujur dan dapat dipecaya</li>\r\n <li><b>Commitment</b></li>\r\n <li>Tekad dan dedikasi untuk mencapai tujuan perusahaan </li>\r\n <li><b>Teamwork</b></li>\r\n <li>Selalu bekerjasama dalam mencapai tujuan</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(24, 13, 'PT Epson Indonesia', 'pt-epson-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/243/images/logo/243_logo_0_87653.png', 'http://epson.co.id/', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan & Tunjangan lain', 'Regular, Senin - Jum\'at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p>Epson is a progressive company, trusted throughout\r\nthe world because of our commitment to customer satisfaction, environmental conservation, individuality\r\nand teamwork. We are confident of our collective skills and meet challenges with innovative and creative\r\nsolutions. Epson has long been perceived as only providing printers but the company is now changing.\r\nCentered around printers, projectors, liquid crystal panels, and the core technologies that link all these\r\nproducts, Epson is putting aside its old image and transforming itself into a \"digital imaging\r\ncompany.\"</p>', '<p>We have a corporate culture that is dynamic, creative and innovative as well as providing an opportunity for you to develop a career with us.</p>'),
(25, 14, 'PT Orix Indonesia Finance', 'pt-orix-indonesia-finance', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/236/images/logo/236_logo_0_7157546.jpg', 'http://www.orix.co.id/', NULL, 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan Lain, Pinjamanm Gigi, Parkir', '', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<p>PT.ORIX Indonesia Finance (ORIF) was established as a joint venture between ORIX Corporation (85%) and Yayasan Kesejahteraan Karyawan Bank Indonesia (15%). Originally established in April 1975, under the name of PT.Orient Bina Usaha Leasing (OBUL), ORIX Indonesia Finance was and still is a pioneer of lease financing in Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p>ORIF has shown its dynamic growth throughout its history, and has risen to become one of Indonesia\'s most innovative financial institutions. ORIF\'s mission is to be a financial innovator to serve its customers by generating totally new values. While closely monitoring emerging trends and projecting future changes, ORIF has positioned itself well to respond flexibly and creatively to opportunities that fall outside its established business framework by providing highly specialized financial services.</p>\r\n<p>ORIF intends to further strengthen its reputation among customers and promote the idea that ORIF is synonymous with the best in financial services.</p>\r\n<p>ORIF now provides direct financing leases and operating leases for a wide array of items. These include office automation (OA) and other information related equipment; machine tools and other industrial machinery; commercial services equipment; and transportation equipment, such as passenger vehicles, commercial vehicles & New Division of Used Car. </p>', '<p>Dear Job Hunter,</p><p><b>Pride, trust and respect is our culture. </b>You will enjoy working with Japanese expatriates in harmonious and mutual respect environment. You will find an international atmosphere in your daily working life, plus a competitive remuneration packages for the best achievers.</p><p>Interesting? visit our website at www.orix.co.id to learn more about our company and find the available vacant positions.</p>'),
(26, 14, 'PT Michael Page Internasional Indonesia', 'pt-michael-page-internasional-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/54913/images/logo/54913_logo_0_43561.jpg', 'http://www.michaelpage.co.id/', NULL, '', '', '', '', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p>Michael Page International is a leading professional recruitment consultancy specialising in the recruitment of permanent, contract and temporary positions on behalf of the world’s top employers. The Group operates through 155 offices in 35 countries worldwide. We have operations in the UK, Continental Europe, Asia Pacific and the Americas and focus on recruiting for the following sectors:</p>\r\n<ul><li>Accounting</li><li>Banking</li><li>Engineering & Manufacturing</li><li>Healthcare and Life Sciences</li><li>Human Resources</li><li>IT & T</li><li>Legal</li><li>Marketing</li><li>Procurement & Supply Chain</li><li>Property & Construction</li><li>Sales</li><li>Secretarial & Office Support</li></ul>', ''),
(27, 15, 'PT Mitra Andal Sejati', 'pt-mitra-andal-sejati', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/18284/images/logo/18284_logo_0_7712451.jpg', '', 'Surakarta (Jawa Tengah) - Pemalang', '', '', '', '', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p>PT Mitra Andal Sejati berdiri sejak tahun 1997 adalah perusahaan yang bergerak dalam bidang Frontliners Services (SPG/Beauty Advisor/MD/Sales), Marketing Activity, Brand Activation dan Event Organizer.</p><p>Salah satu klien yang bekerjasama dengan kami yaitu PT Unilever Indonesia, Tbk.</p>', ''),
(28, 15, 'SCG', 'scg', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/26390/images/logo/26390_logo_0_512587.jpg', 'http://www.scg.com/', 'http://www.scg.com', 'Formil (Kemeja+dasi)', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lainnya', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p><b>SCG</b> (Siam Cement Group) is a Thailand-based company which has 3 core businesses namely SCG Cement - Building Materials, SCG Chemicals, SCG Paper. SCG has been operating in Indonesia since 1995 and has a total of 18 companies in Indonesia eg. Jayamix, Kia Keramic, Kokoh, SSK, Pipe and Precast etc.SCG conducts its businesses in line with good corporate governance and the principles of sustainable development. The Group commits itself to its longstanding tradition of organizational and employee development, which creates higher value to all parties concerned. Beyond this, SCG pledges its commitment to contributing to the sustainable progress of the communities where it operates</p><p>SCG began business operation in Indonesia since 1995 by opening a trading office which mainly focused on trading and market research, and gradually expand investment in diversified businesses such as PVC, ceramic tiles, and join venture with partner in building materials business. In 2011-2012, SCG intensely invested in array of businesses in Indonesia to pursue the company vision to become a sustainable leader in ASEAN. Today, SCG has more than 5,700 employees in Indonesia and total of 20 companies in many industries including petrochemicals, cement, building materials, and distribution.</p>', '<p>We believe that our employees are a valuable asset and that every person in our company is a key player in helping the company to reach the pinnacle of success. We are looking for professionals who are motivated, dynamic, responsible and disciplined willing to come forward and join us and be one of our great team.</p>'),
(29, 16, 'PT Svarna Dipa', 'pt-svarna-dipa', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/19511/images/logo/19511_logo_0.jpg', '', 'Bandar Lampung (Lampung)', 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Mondays - Saturdays', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<p>PT. SVARNA DIPA adalah Perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang Distributor Elektronik yang sedang berkembang pesat yang berlokasi di kawasan Cengkareng Jakarta Barat, Membuka Lowongan kerja untuk posisi sebagai berikut:</p>', '<p>Kami bangga dalam budaya tim kami yang kuat saling percaya, belajar, berbagi, kepedulian dan perhatian. Termasuk menyediakan lingkungan kerja yang nyaman dan kondusif dan meningkatkan profesional dan pribadi pertumbuhan staf kami. Kami mencari professional muda yang termotivasi, dinamis, mandiri, bertanggung jawab dan disiplin bersedia untuk maju dan bergabung dengan kami dan menjadi salah satu tim yang hebat kami.</p>'),
(30, 16, 'PT Bukit Perak', 'pt-bukit-perak', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/27813/images/logo/27813_logo_0.jpg', 'http://www.beacorp.com', 'Bandar Lampung (Lampung)', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', '-', 'Sabtu, atau memerlukan shift', '200 - 500 Pekerja', '<p>PT. Bukit Perak adalah Perusahaan yang bergerak di bidang Manufacturing Toilet Soap & Personal Care product, berlokasi di Jl. Raya Semarang Kendal km.10,5, Semarang - Indonesia.</p><p>Berdiri  sejak tahun 1959, kami senantiasa melakukan pembenahan baik terhadap sarana maupun prasarana pabrik serta inovasi-inovasi atas produk yang kami hasilkan. Dan sampai dengan saat ini 80?ri hasil produksi kami adalah untuk pasar Global seperti negara-negara di Afrika, Timur Tengah, Amerika Latin, Asia, Kanada dan 20?alah untuk pasar domestik yang terdiri dari body lotion, saun, detergent powder, hotel aminities dll.</p>', '<p>Established in 1959, rich in history. Our motto is Quality with values.<br> Our company culture respects, values and encourages each individual\'s personal and professional growth.<br> When you join us you\'re not just an employee, you\'re part of the family </p>'),
(31, 14, 'PT Abacus Cash Solution', 'pt-abacus-cash-solution', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/50992/images/logo/50992_logo_0_710226.jpg', 'https://www.abacuscash.co.id/', 'Denpasar (Bali), Jakarta Raya, Kendari (Sulawesi Tenggara), Makassar (Sulawesi Selatan),', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '2000 - 5000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed><strong>PT Abacus Cash Solution</strong> adalah perusahaan yang bergerak dibidang jasa layanan cash management. Saat ini perusahaan kami sedang melakukan pengembangan cabang sebagai hasil dari perkembangan usaha yang semakin signifikan. Dengan dukungan dari professional dibidang nya sehingga kami mengalami perkembangan usaha yang semakin lebih baik dalam dunia usaha ini.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><ul><li xss=removed>Kami memiliki budaya perusahaan yang kreatif dan inovatif yang membuat karyawan kami bahagia – work hard and play hard!</li><li xss=removed>Kami memberikan pengertian yang jelas mengenai apa prioritas bisnis perusahaan</li></ul><p></p>'),
(32, 14, 'PT Mitracitra Mandirioffset', 'pt-mitracitra-mandirioffset', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/13065/images/logo/13065_logo_0_363618.jpg', 'http://msepaper.com/mcmo/', 'Mojokerto (Jawa Timur), Sidoarjo (Jawa Timur)', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, BPJS Ketenagakerjaan', 'Sabtu atau memerlukan shift', '1000 - 2000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed><strong>PENGUMUMAN :<br> PT <strong>Mitracitra Mandirioffset</strong> tidak pernah memungut biaya apapun dalam proses rekrutmen.<br> PT <strong>Mitracitra Mandirioffset</strong> tidak pernah bekerja sama dengan travel agent / biro perjalanan tertentu dalam proses rekrutmen.<br> Apabila Anda diminta untuk membayar sejumlah uang dalam bentuk pembayaran tiket pesawat dan hotel atau akomodasi lainnya agar diabaikan.<br> Jangan memberikan data pribadi atau data keuangan Anda kepada siapapun.<br> Jika membutuhkan klarifikasi lebih lanjut dapat langsung menghubungi PT <strong>Mitracitra Mandirioffset</strong></strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>====================================================================</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Mitra Group merupakan perusahaan percetakan dan kemasan berbahan kertas yang bermula dari sebuah usaha percetakan di Surabaya-Indonesia berdiri pada tahun 1976 dan berkembang menjadi salah satu perusahaan percetakan dan kemasan swasta terbesar, yang didukung oleh divisi kertas miliknya.<br> Mitra Group terdiri dari PT. Mitracitra Mandirioffset yang beroperasi di Sidoarjo dan Mojokerto dan PT. Mitra Surya Eratama Packaging yang beroperasi di Tangerang. Di tahun 2010, Group Mitra membangun pabrik kertas untuk memasok kebutuhan kertas berkualitas tinggi, yaitu PT. Mega Surya Eratama yang berlokasi di Mojosari, Mojokerto.<br> Mitra Group terus berkembang dengan berfokus pada pengembangan teknologi, peralatan, sumber daya serta proses kerja sehingga dapat meningkatkan efisiensi, inovasi, kualitas produk dan pelayanan kepada kliennya. Mitra Group juga menumbuhkan kerjasama jangka panjang pada setiap customer dan supplier utama untuk mencapai tujuan yang saling menguntungkan.<br> Dengan pengalaman yang sudah lebih dari 40 tahun kami berkembang menjadi ahli dibidang percetakan, dan terus mengembangkan berbagai inovasi agar dapat melayani customer kami dengan lebih baik. Mitra sudah tersertifikasi oleh beberapa standart. Semua ini untuk mencapai Visi perusahaan, menjadi yang terbesar di Industri Cetak & Kemasan di Indonesia.<br> Service Excellence, World’s Quality Products, Safe Operation, merupakan salah satu Misi kami dalam mencapai visi tersebut. Seluruh kemampuan kami curahkan, seluruh tenaga kami kerahkan hanya untuk satu tujuan kami: kepuasan pelanggan adalah di atas segala-galanya</div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT. Mitracitra Mandirioffset merupakan salah satu industri cetak dan kemasan terbesar di Indonesia. Hampir semua cetakan pernah kami kerjakan dan sekitar 75?rkualitas ekspor sedangkan sisanya untuk pasar lokal. Sumber daya manusia merupakan salah satu aset penting dalam perusahaan. Terus menerus kami tingkatkan kemampuannya, sehingga menjadi satu harmonisasi antara teknologi dengan sumber daya yang memadai. PT. Mitracitra Mandirioffset  aktif mengikutkan karyawan kedalam berbagai macam training untuk meningkatkan skill dan knowledge karyawan. Kesehatan dan kesejahteraan karyawan merupakan salah satu prioritas perusahaan  untuk menunjang hal tersebut kami mengikutsertakan seluruh karyawan dalam BPJS Kesehatan dan Ketenagakerjaan. Kami juga memberikan kesempatan luas untuk mengembangkan karir di perusahaan.</div><p></p>'),
(33, 17, 'PT Ekamita Arahtegar', 'pt-ekamita-arahtegar', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/15982/images/logo/15982_logo_0_90417.jpg', 'http://www.mitrakeluarga.com/', 'Depok (Jawa Barat), Tangerang (Banten)', 'Uniform', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Pinjaman, Parkir', 'Monday - Friday 08.00 - 16.00, Saturday 08.00 - 13.00', 'Lebih dari 5000', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Mitra Keluarga  saat ini memiliki 16 cabang yang tersebar di beberapa wilayah strategis di kota-kota besar di Indonesia, yaitu Bekasi Barat, Kemayoran, Surabaya, Kelapa Gading, Bekasi Timur, Depok, Tegal, Waru, Cikarang, Cibubur, Kalideres dan Gading Serpong.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Pembukaan rumah sakit dilandasi adanya kebutuhan akan pelayanan kesehatan bertaraf internasional di Jakarta pada khususnya. Dengan dilengkapi peralatan yang modern & canggih serta didukung oleh sumber daya manusia yang baik dan terus mengembangkan diri, dan untuk menjaga kualitas pelayanan, kami juga telah melengkapi diri dengan Akreditasi 16 Bidang Pelayanan serta Sertifikasi ISO 9001: 2000. dan sistem yang terintegrasi.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Terima kasih kami ucapkan kepada pasien-pasien serta perusahaan kerjasama kami yang telah mempercayakan layanan kesehatannya kepada kami dari seluruh wilayah Indonesia. Kami berusaha memberikan pelayanan yang terbaik bagi Anda dan keluarga.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Kami percaya bahwa karyawan adalah aset berharga kami dan bahwa setiap orang di perusahaan kami adalah pemain kunci dalam membantu perusahaan untuk mencapai puncak kesuksesan. Kami mencari professional yang termotivasi, dinamis, bertanggung jawab dan disiplin bersedia untuk maju dan bergabung dengan kami dan menjadi salah satu tim hebat kami.</div><p></p>'),
(34, 17, 'PT Artolite Indah Mediatama', 'pt-artolite-indah-mediatama', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/2368/images/logo/2368_logo_0_128385.jpg', '', 'Depok (Jawa Barat)', '', '', '', '', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=\"removed\"><div>ARTOLITE adalah Pabrik Armature  lampu terkemuka di seluruh Indonesia yang berdiri sejak tahun 1976  berlokasi di Cimanggis Depok Jawa Barat dengan luas area lebih kurang 25.000 m2  mempunyai karyawan yang sudah berpengalaman dibidangnya mempunyai Distributor tunggal yaitu PT.Abetama Sempurna dengan cabang di Kota Besar seluruh Indonesia.</div><div> </div><div>Kami percaya suasana yang harmonis akan membuat kami bekerja lebih optimal. Namun kami serius dengan KESUKSESAN. Kami ingin memberikan dampak positif bagi dunia ini dengan memberikan “WOW” bagi orang lain.</div><div> </div><div>ARTOLITE INDAH MEDIATAMA adalah produsen armature lampu terkemuka yang sudah diakui di seluruh indonesia dan sudah mempunyai :</div><ul><li>Menganut ISO 9001 – 2015</li><li>Menciptakan Produk SNI yang sudah diakui di Indonesia</li><li>Mendapat Europe Award Paris 1990</li></ul><div> </div><div>Jika Anda tidak hanya ingin bekerja, namun juga belajar bersama menambah pengalaman, kami tunggu RESUME Anda. Kunjungi kami di www.artolite.co.id</div></div><p></p></div>', ''),
(35, 18, 'PT Laboratorium Medio Pratama', 'pt-laboratorium-medio-pratama', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/45431/images/logo/45431_logo_0_16631.jpg', 'http://www.labmedio.com/profile.html', 'Tangerang (Banten) - Gading Serpong', 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Parkir, Ketenagakerjaan', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Laboratorium Medio Pratama sebagai laboratorium uji analisa dan monitoring lingkungan, terletak di wilayah berkembang yaitu Gading Serpong, Tangerang, sebagai sarana untuk menjawab, membantu, mengatasi, dan memberikan solusi terbaik dari seluruh permintaan pasar uji analisa lingkungan yang ada pada saat ini. Laboratorium Medio Pratama sebagai laboratorium uji analisa dan monitoring lingkungan akan terus berupaya untuk melakukan yang terbaik bagi pelanggan, dengan segala dukungan baik dari internal maupun eksternal</div><p></p></div>', ''),
(36, 18, 'PT Foamindo Industri Uretan', 'pt-foamindo-industri-uretan', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/30464/images/logo/30464_logo_0_6978496.jpg', '', 'Tangerang (Banten)', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lainnya, Parkir', 'Sabtu atau memerlukan shift', '200 - 500 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>PT. Foamindo Industri Uretan is a polyurethane (PU) manufacturing company that was established in the year 1971. Considered as one of the market leaders in the PU industry and with a diverse customer base, PT. Foamindo Industri Uretan continues to grow and innovates itself with the goal of delivering high quality products and meet customer satisfaction. </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=\"removed\">Well equipped with the latest foam making technologies and machineries that are capable of annual production of 300.000 m3, our manufacturing facilities enable us to service the Indonesian market reliably and effectively. In addition, we are strategically located in the midst of an industrial zone which enable us to fulfill orders in fast and economical manner.<br> We are committed to provide the best quality products for our customers and it is fittingly proven through the rigorous audits that we passed to achieve our ISO 9001:2000 certification. This certification ensures that our process and quality comply with the international industry standard.</div><p></p>'),
(37, 19, 'PT Nutech Integrasi', 'pt-nutech-integrasi', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/4952/images/logo/4952_logo_0_541112.jpg', 'http://www.nutech-integrasi.com/', 'Jakarta Raya', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatanm Tunjangan lain, Bantuan Pendidikan, Parkir, Jamsostek, Pajak ditanggung perus', 'Office Support: Regular (Monday - Friday), Based on Project', '200 - 500 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed><strong>PT. Nutech Integrasi was formed in early 2006. Since then the company concentrate as system integrator in ICT total solution.</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Nutech is dedicated to deliver the best result by furnishing the industries such as transportation, telecomunication, financial institution, logistic, health, retail, education, travel & tourism, utilities and many other with innovative products and services. </strong></div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div><strong>VISION</strong></div><div> </div><div>To become a strong and reliable end to end smart card solution provider in the country as well as in the region</div><div> </div><div><strong>MISSION</strong></div><div> </div> To bring smart technology towards a better life <div> </div><div><strong>VALUE</strong></div><div> </div><div>Integrity, Passion, Honesty</div></div><p></p>');
INSERT INTO `perusahaan` (`id`, `industri_id`, `perusahaan_name`, `url`, `logo`, `website`, `alamat_perusahaan`, `fashion`, `bahasa`, `tunjangan`, `waktu_kerja`, `ukuran_perusahaan`, `description`, `why_join_us`) VALUES
(38, 19, 'PT MEKA EDUVERSITY KOMUNIKASI', 'pt-meka-eduveristy', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/66482/images/logo/66482_logo_0_635438.jpg', 'https://renacel.org/', '', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', '', 'Six day per week', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Every Company Has A Story To Tell.</div><div> </div><div>We are a Jakarta-based Interactive Web Solution & Marketing Company, with a team of experienced Business Analyst, Project Managers, Web Designers & Developers. Our web solutions are implemented with a focus on Customer Acquisition, Brand Identity & Revenue growth.<br><br> Our Approach</div><div><br> At Renacel, our work is centered around the brand. Creating an emotional connection between our client and their audience starts and ends with the brand experience. We have a deep understanding of brands and the ways in which their attributes can be expressed—whether through text, image or multimedia. We work closely with our clients to uncover these attributes and communicate the core messages that bridge the gap between the brand and its audience.</div><div> </div><div>As a full service interactive design studio, we help our clients achieve all of their goals by making sure the brand experience is fully realized, from the planning stages to the final implementation. Our designers and developers create compelling solutions that target our clients’ objectives and their audience’s needs by finding a true balance between form and function.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div>Passionate and Dedicated Team</div><div><br> We only hire digital service passionate people to grow along with the rapid development of digital technology. We need people who could catch up, stay above the wave and keep surfing to give the best services and products for you.</div><div>Our team consist of digital technology enthusiast, a sedulous web designer, a tireless web engineer, a loveable finance sister, a matronly digital marketing manager and a humble tech-support guy. Together under the same vision, we create a better solution, insight, ideas, and support for all of your digital assets, so you can focus in other things that seems more important to you.</div></div><p></p>'),
(39, 19, 'PT Gamatechno Indonesia (Group of Companies)', 'pt-gamatechno', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/14831/images/logo/14831_logo_0_6256989.jpg', 'http://www.gamatechno.com/', 'Yogyakarta (Yogyakarta) - Kota Yogyakarta', 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Olahraga, Achievment bonus', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed><div>at Gamatechno Group, <strong>Everyone\'s Invited!</strong></div><div> </div><div>Hi everyone, PT Gamatechno Indonesia adalah holding beberapa perusahaan teknologi berbasis riset dari Indonesia yg berfokus ke pengembangan ekosistem IT SmartCity Solution.</div><div> </div><div>Kami yakin salah satu cara hebat melayani Indonesia adalah dengan memperkuat cara para pelaku bisnis bekerja lebih efisien, membantu para pengambil kebijakan untuk memecahkan masalah mereka untuk melayani masyarakat dengan lebih baik.</div><div> </div><div>Making Indonesia\'s Smarter Needs Everyone To Join!</div><div> </div><div>_You Make Our Team Stronger_</div></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Tiga hal yang unik di Gamatechno (Smart City Software Solution Group of Companies):</div><ul><li><strong>Shaping Everyone To Contribute</strong>, buat para applicants... lets collaborate dengan para super engineers kami disini. Kamu akan bekerja bersama, bertukar pikiran, saling belajar satu sama lain untuk berkontribusi membangun produk smart city solution.</li><li><strong>Limitless Career</strong>, buat kamu yg tipikal challenger, tidak ada hitungan belasan tahun utk dapat masuk ke Management Team. Kami memiliki management role yang sangat luas. Di Gamatechno, kami punya 3 anak perusahaan dan belasan produk startup, dengan 3 business unit yang tersedia bagi para pemimpin-pemimpin muda berbakat!</li><li><strong>Less Bureaucracy</strong>, meski telah berdiri lebih dari 14thn, kamu bisa kapan saja berdiskusi dengan Tim Direksi, Tim Manajemen, para Senior Engineers/ Engineers di lintas anak perusahaan, suasana kerja yang khas Indonesia (kekeluargaan yg tinggi) dipadukan dengan di kecepatan sebuah start up technology semua ada disini.</li></ul><p></p>'),
(40, 19, 'PT Infolog Solutions Indonesia', 'pt-infolog', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/54810/images/logo/54810_logo_0_587626.jpg', 'http://www.infolog.com.sg/', 'Bandung (Jawa Barat), Jakarta Barat (Jakarta Raya)', 'Smart casual', 'Indonesia, Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lain, Gigi, Penglihatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div>Infolog is an industry-leader in providing software application for Distribution, Logistics & Supply Chain Industry. Infolog provides suite of product called \"<strong>Infolog Logistics Suite\"</strong> which covers end-to-end Supply Chain needs. Infolog integrate all material handling equipment (RFID, Pick/Put To Light, Voice Technology, Barcode Scanning Mobile Computer, Robotic) into one suite of solution to increase the productivity and efficiency of your operation.</div><div> </div><div>Infolog focuses and helps customer to identify and close gaps that is not covered by both ERP package and established supply chain solution available in market. Infolog strive to innovate and develop this solution to cover the gap and bring efficiency of customer operation and real time visibility for their management.</div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><strong>Our People</strong><br>  </div><div>They are our asset and also what make us stand out from the rest. Passionate about their work, serious on what they are doing, creative and hard working with right attitude.</div><div> </div><div>Our senior team came from Logistics & Supply Chain IT industry with 10 over years of experience. This is the elite team that drive the company forward. They are supported by a junior team that specially selected for their role and some of them are top student from well known universities in this region.</div><div> </div><div><strong>Our values </strong></div><div> </div><div><div>We believe every customer is unique. We have the following principles on operating our business:</div><ul><li>Respect our customer & Individual</li><li>Integrity & Do what is Right</li><li>Commitment to Excellence</li><li>Strive to Continuously Innovate & Give New Idea</li></ul><div> </div></div><div> </div><p></p>'),
(41, 19, 'PT Acetris Formatika', 'pt-acetris-formatika', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/35240/images/logo/35240_logo_0_6044388.jpg', '', 'Jakarta Raya - Kebon Jeruk', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lainnya, Parkir', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div><strong>PT Acetris Formatika </strong>is a fast-growing IT Consultant and Software Developer. We provide the best integrated and comprehensive Business Applications, which includes Enterprise Resource Planning System, Financial Accounting System, Production & Manufacturing System, Human Resource & Payroll System, Restaurant Information Sytem, Business Intelligence Application, etc.</div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', ''),
(42, 8, 'PT Triputra Investindo Arya (Triputra Group)', 'pt-tripura-investindo-arya', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/11381/images/logo/11381_logo_0_20914.png', 'http://www.triputra-group.com/', 'Jakarta Raya', 'Bisnis (Kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Gigi, Glasses, transport, COP', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', 'Lebih dari 5000', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed><strong>PENGUMUMAN :</strong></div><div xss=removed><br><strong>PT Triputra Investindo Arya (Triputra Group) tidak pernah memungut biaya apapun dalam proses rekrutmen.<br> PT Triputra Investindo Arya (Triputra Group) tidak pernah bekerja sama dengan travel agent / biro perjalanan tertentu dalam proses rekrutmen.<br> Apabila Anda diminta untuk membayar sejumlah uang dalam bentuk pembayaran tiket pesawat dan hotel atau akomodasi lainnya agar diabaikan.<br> Jangan memberikan data pribadi atau data keuangan Anda kepada siapapun.<br> Jika membutuhkan klarifikasi lebih lanjut dapat langsung menghubungi PT Triputra Investindo Arya (Triputra Group)</strong></div><div xss=removed>=======================================================</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Tahun 1998 Triputra Group awalnya didirikan sebagai induk dari Adira Mobil & Adira Finance Tahun 2004 Adira Finance dijual ke Bank Danamon, Tbk dengan tujuan pengembangan dimasa yang akan datang dan rencana diversifikasi dari Triputra Group Hasil dari kesepakatan ini kemudian di gunakan untuk memperluas lini bisnis di sektor-sektor industri yang lebih menjanjikan.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Saat ini Triputra Group memiliki empat lini bisnis antara lain Agribusiness, Manufacturing, Mining, Trading & Services, dengan jumlah karyawan lebih dari 60.000.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Triputra Group melalui keempat lini bisnisnya memiliki Visi to become a group of best managed companies, hal ini sejalan dengan Misi-nya agar dapat terus berkontribusi bagi daya saing bangsa. Untuk itu, Triputra Group menggerakan semua bisnis dengan motto Excellence through People and Process disertai dengan Value / Triputra DNA yang ada di setiap Insan Triputra, yaitu Integrity & Ethics, Excellence, Compassion & Humility.</div><div> </div><div>Triputra DNA merupakan Guiding Values bagi Insan Triputra untuk mewujudnyatakan reason of being Triputra Group yakni “Ada karena Indonesia, oleh Indonesia, dan untuk Indonesia”.</div><div><br> Sebagai Guiding Values, maka Triputra DNA dinyatakan sebagai pemersatu dari keberagaman di Triputra Group, sehingga apapun jabatannya; dimanapun perusahaannya; dan sampai kapanpun Insan Triputra akan memiliki keseragaman values. Hal ini juga akan memudahkan kesamaan bahasa dan pemahaman yang pada akhirnya akan mendorong efektivitas sosialisasi dan internalisasi dalam lingkup Triputra Group.<br>  </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><strong>Our Motto</strong></div><ul><li>Excellence through People and Process</li></ul><div><strong>Our Vision</strong></div><ul><li>To become a group of best managed companies</li></ul><div><strong>Our Mission</strong></div><ul><li>Contributing to the nation\'s competitive edge</li></ul><div> </div><div><strong>Our DNA Value:</strong></div><ul><li>INTEGRITY & ETHICS</li></ul><div>             as for being a Good Corporate Citizen</div><div>            (Accountability/Fairness/Responsibility)</div><ul><li>EXCELLENCE</li></ul><div>              mindset as to bring the Utmost Customer Satisfaction</div><div>              (Passionate/Productive Paranoia/Kaizen)</div><ul><li>COMPASSION</li></ul><div>              to creating a Better Comunity</div><div>             (Sympathy/Empathy/Sincerity)</div><ul><li>HUMILITY</li></ul><div>              by showing Respect for Individual</div><div>             (Self-awareness/Respectfulness/Gratefulness)</div><div> </div><div> </div><div><strong>Triputra Philosophy</strong><ul><li>Integrity and high work ethics</li><li>Synergy and respect for the individual</li><li>Utmost customer satisfaction</li><li>Excellence through continuous innovation</li><li>Social concern and environmental friendly</li></ul></div><div> </div><p></p>'),
(43, 3, 'PT INDIE MARKETINDO CERIA', 'pt-indie-marketindo', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/160657/images/logo/160657_logo_0_962857.jpg', '', 'Bandung (Jawa Barat) - Mekar Wangi', 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Indonesia', '', 'Regular, Senin - Jumat', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Kami adalah perusahaan konsultan yang berlokasi di Bandung dan bekerjasama dengan beberapa perusahaan Retail dan Manufacture serta E-Commerce. kami mengundang para kandidat terbaik untuk bergabung dan menjadi anggota tim yang berdedikasi untuk memajukan perusahaan serta dapat meningkatkan kemampuan kandidat sampai di level tertinggi.  </div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed>Kami percaya bahwa karyawan adalah aset berharga kami dan bahwa setiap orang di perusahaan kami adalah pemain kunci dalam membantu perusahaan untuk mencapai puncak kesuksesan. Kami mencari professional yang termotivasi, dinamis, bertanggung jawab dan disiplin bersedia untuk maju dan bergabung dengan kami dan menjadi salah satu tim hebat kami.</div></div><p></p>'),
