(96, 22, 'Valiram Group (PT Dunia Luxindo)', 'valiram-group', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/55309/images/logo/55309_logo_0_85466.jpg', 'http://valiram.com/', 'Jakarta Selatan (Jakarta Raya)', 'Formal & Fashionable', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan', '9.00 AM - 6.00 PM for Back office, Shifting hours for operational', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>The Valiram Group was established in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia in 1935, originally specializing in the textile trade. Today, Valiram is Southeast Asia\'s leading luxury goods and specialist retailer with presence in Australia, Indonesia, Macau, Malaysia, Philippines, Russia, Singapore and Thailand. The Group operates over 320 stores, representing in excess of 150 brands across various categories including fashion and accessories, timepieces and jewellery, leather goods, fragrance and cosmetics and confectionary.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><ul><li>You will be part of our journey in growing our retail footprint to be the ULTIMATE BRAND OF BRANDS.</li><li>You will be  joining one of the fastest growing companies in Southeast Asia.</li><li>You will have a wealth of career and development opportunities across categories and countries.</li><li>You will be part of a dynamic, fast changing and challenging work environment.</li><li>You will get the chance to celebrate the existence of luxury in a unique way via our employee engagement activities and our attractive brand privileges.</li></ul><p></p>'),
(97, 22, 'PT Indo Avatar Sejati', 'pt-indo-avatar-sejati', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/15105/images/logo/15105_logo_0_336570.jpg', 'https://allumia.co.id/', 'Jawa Barat', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Insentive', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT. INDO AVATAR SEJATI adalah perusahaan teknologi LED yang memiliki spesialisasi di bidang penerangan LED, yang di tunjuk resmi oleh TCL sebagai distributor di indonesia . Teknologi penerangan LED ini memiliki efisiensi 50 – 90 % dibanding dengan penerangan konvensional selama ini seperti Fluorescent ( lampu hemat energy ), Halogen dan lampu pijar. <div> </div><div>Produk Lampu TCL ini telah mendapatkan sertifikasi ISO 9001: 2000 dan berbagai sertifikasi internasional seperti GS, CE, EMC, UL, FCC, Energy-Star, CCC. Saat ini kami memiliki berbagai produk penerangan LED yang dapat memenuhi segala kebutuhan penerangan anda, baik indoor maupun outdoor.</div><div> </div><div>Sebagai salah satu usaha mendukung program pemerintah dan dunia dalam penghematan energy , mengurangi polusi dan gerakan Go Green pemakaian lampu LED sangat dianjurkan, karena lampu LED tidak memiliki filamen seperti lampu pijar , atau zat beracun seperti gas merkuri pada lampu fluorecent.</div><div> </div><div>Dengan dukungan anda sebagai klien dan mitra kami, bersama – sama kita mulai gerakan dunia yang lebih hijau dan melestarikan bumi ini.</div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed><strong>Mengapa harus memilih TCL LED :</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><ul><li xss=removed>TCL merupakan global brand yang memiliki standard kualitas produk yang tinggi</li><li xss=removed>TCL selalu memberikan inovasi dan tehnology terdepan disertai dengan peningkatan kualitas produk</li><li xss=removed>Mendapat sertifikat internasional ISO9001 2000, CE, ROHS, SAA, CCC, FCC, UL</li><li xss=removed>Harga yang kompetitif</li></ul><p></p>'),
(98, 11, 'PT. Megah Estetika Perkasa', 'pt-megah-estetika-perkasa', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/52928/images/logo/52928_logo_0_7554620.jpg', 'http://www.dermaster-indonesia.com/', 'Jakarta Pusat (Jakarta Raya)', 'Formil (Kemeja+Dasi)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lain', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT. MEGAH ESTETIKA PERKASA adalah perusahaan yang bergerak dibidang jasa klinik kecantikan dengan nama klinik Dermaster Aesthetic and Hair Clinic. Dermaster klinik sendiri merupakan sebuah klinik kecantikan yang didirikan pada tahun 2002 oleh Dr. Kwon Han Jin di Seoul, Gang Nam Samsung Dong. Dermaster klinik yang didirikan oleh Dr. Kwon Han Jin kini berkembang dengan pesat, sekarang ini franchise Dermaster klinik sudah ada di negara Malaysia, Vietnam, Phillipines, HongKong, Taiwan, Thailand, Los Angeles, hingga USA.Klinik kecantikan yang sudah tersebar di negara-negara besar ini sekarang telah membuka beberapa cabang di kota Jakarta, yaitu di Mangga Besar, Pondok Indah, Pantai Indah Kapuk, Kemang dan Makassar. Selain itu, kami akan membuka cabang kembali dalam waktu dekat.<br> Kami memiliki para ahli terbaik yang bergerak dibidangnya masing-masing yang sudah dipercaya oleh Dr. Kwon Han Jin. Selain itu kami juga menyiapkan dokter-dokter serta para perawat lainnya yang sudah sangat terlatih dan secara langsung dilatih dari Korea agar semua sistem dan cara pengerjaannya sesuai dan sama dengan prosedur yang ada di Dermaster lainnya.<br> Dermaster sangat mengutamakan kenyamanan para pasien kami ketika berada di Dermaster Clinic, pasien akan merasakan sendiri perbedaan interior dan eksterior yang sangat nyaman dan berbeda dibandingkan klinik-klinik lainnya di Indonesia. Selain itu kami juga menyediakan ruang khusus bagi tamu VIP ketika berkunjung ke Dermaster Clinic.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Kami percaya bahwa karyawan adalah aset berharga dan bahwa setiap orang di perusahaan kami adalah pemain kunci dalam membantu perusahaan untuk mencapai puncak kesuksesan. Kami mencari para profesional yang termotivasi, dinamis, bertanggung jawab dan disiplin bersedia untuk maju dan bergabung dengan kami dan menjadi salah satu anggota tim kami yang hebat.</div><p></p>'),
(99, 8, 'PT Forisa Nusapersada', 'pt-forisa-nusapersada', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/7400/images/logo/7400_logo_0_399650.jpg', 'http://www.forisa.co.id/', 'Bandung (Jawa Barat), Cirebon (Jawa Barat), Gorontalo, Sulawesi Selatan', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Tunjangan lain', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '2000 - 5000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div>PT. Forisa Nusapersada was established in 1995, focusing on the production and marketing of various beverages, particularly in the form of pulverized powder, that are of high quality. Forisa’s head office is in Jakarta, with a wide distribution network for its products to domestic and international market (Afrika, Australia, Brunei, Hong Kong, Malaysia, Philippines, Singapore). We are now considered to be one of the strongest players in the country’s beverage industry.</div><div><br> The Company is always committed to creativity and innovation, determined to always satisfy the direct consumers. Our popular brands are POP ICE, NUTRIJELL, ANGET SARI  and SISRI TEA.</div><div>Culture and work of habit Forisa totally lead the team in maximal effort to achieve company vision and mission, our values :</div><div><br> 1. God center: always express gratitude and surrender all our endeavors to God Almighty<br> 2. Loyalty: Sense of belonging and caring about one another. Responsible for every step and decision we make.<br> 3. Integrity: We expect all our employees to uphold honesty, discipline, involvement, commitment and consistency in our day-to-day business activities.<br> 4. Team work: Good cooperation within all team members.<br> 5. Innovative: Creativity and perseverance in producing the best products to help raise the well being of our society<br> 6. Keen to Positive attitude : A family atmosphere, humble and willing to accept critic from outside as well  as within the organization</div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<ul><li>Culture and values</li><li>Growth prospects</li></ul>'),
(100, 14, 'PT Indodax', 'pt-indodax', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/175063/images/logo/175063_logo_0_572925.jpg', 'http://www.indodax.com/', 'Jakarta Selatan (Jakarta Raya)', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Parkir', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div>Indodax is an online platform where you can buy and sell Bitcoin, Ethereum</div><div>and other Digital Assets in Indonesia. Currently we are the biggest digital asset exchange in Indonesia.</div><div>Our Vision is to provide everyone with secure and convinient access to Blockhain based digital asset and our mission is to become the largest, most trusted, and secure digital asset exchange in Indonesia</div></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>We are an expanding Start up company, in Indodax we value trust, intergrity, and team culture. Here you can develop yourself dan skills,and we\'re opened to new ideas, keep on making new improvement.</div><div> </div><p></p>'),
(101, 19, 'Nurosoft Consulting (PT. Nuroho Software Consulting)', 'nurusoft-consulting', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/59263/images/logo/59263_logo_0_468358.jpg', 'https://nurosoft.id/', 'Surabaya (Jawa Timur)', 'Semi kasual', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Our team is our greatest asset, and we believe that our unique approach to software engineering and dedication to customer satisfaction makes us your perfect technology partner.We are composed of highly skilled software, web, mobile app developers, who take pride in applying software development best practices and delivering excellence to our clients. Literally, to be “the house of everything good”.</div><div> </div><div>https://nurosoft.id</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Our team loves coming to work. With a fast paced and exciting startup environment, working at Nurosoft is interesting, rewarding and fun. ??There are a lot of opportunities for growth and learning, without missing out on the fun.</div><div><br> Whether it’s our annual hackathon challange that improves your coding and business skills, games & quizzes, or our occasional “tumpengan” for celebrations, our workplace will keep you entertained and engaged.<br>  </div><div>Join our team, working together with the smartest peers in the IT industry to solve organizations’ most challenging problems. Unleash your talents and apply now!</div><p></p>'),
(102, 19, 'PT Mindo Small Business Solutions', 'pt-mindo-small-bussiness-solutions', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/21474/images/logo/21474_logo_0_6385826.jpg', '', 'Yogyakarta (Yogyakarta)', 'Kasual (kaos)', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Mindo is a fast growing business consultancy company based in Yogyakarta, Indonesia. Mindo serves clients from all over the world with a wealth of experience in web development, IT consultancy, Server Maintenance, APP Development, API Development, CRM Systems, QA Services, Data Entry, Billing / Accounting and Customer Service. For Employees, Mindo offers a professional and friendly work environment that focuses on employee retention and career progression. Employees are encouraged to take part in office sports and recreational activities, and English and career advancement courses are free for all employees. Apply today and join the Mindo family... </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><ul><li><div>Fun and friendly work environment</div></li><li><div>You will work with new & latest technologies</div></li><li><div>You will cooperate with a reliable team and support clients from overseas such as USA, France, Australia, Thailand, Vietnam</div></li><li><div>Fresh graduates, college drop-outs, coding boot camp alumni are welcome to apply</div></li><li><div>We conduct opportunity for all employee to develop their career</div></li><li><div>Free English class (from Beginner to Advanced)</div></li><li><div>Free flow of snacks, drinks, and coffee</div></li><li><div>Many clubs you can join with (Basketball, Futsal, Badminton, Movie, Foodies, History, etc).</div></li><li><div>Baby born gift</div></li><li><div>3 Months maternity paid leave</div></li><li><div>1 week of paternity paid leave</div></li><li><div>12 days annual paid leave</div></li><li><div>Emergency leave available in case of unexpected events</div></li><li><div>BPJS Ketenagakerjaan & BPJS Kesehatan</div></li><li><div>Game room experience to have fun (with PlayStation4 and Xbox)</div></li><li><div>Regular Team building outings</div></li><li><div>Possibility to travel to overseas client</div></li></ul><p></p>'),
(103, 15, 'PT Casco Sea', 'pt-casco-sea', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/47064/images/logo/47064_logo_0_807312.jpg', 'http://www.cascoauto.com/', 'Batam (Kepulauan Riau)', 'Formil (Kemeja+Dasi)', 'Indonesia', 'BPJS', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed><strong>PT CASCO SEA is part of a global operating concern with ca. 3200 employees. Our facility is located in Batam and we design, produce, and sell innovative electronic automotive components for all prominent automotive manufacturers</strong></div><p></p></div>', '<p>Let\'s Join us !<br></p>'),
(104, 24, 'PT Binawan Inti Utama', 'pt-binawan-inti-utama', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/2568/images/logo/2568_logo_0_195502.png', '', 'Jakarta Raya', '', '', '', '', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT. BINAWAN INTI UTAMA adalah perusahaan yang sudah berpengalaman sejak tahun 1979 yang bergerak dalam bidang penempatan kerja ke luar negeri khususnya tenaga kerja berkeahlian tertentu untuk bekerja di negara tertentu</div><p></p></div>', ''),
(105, 30, 'PT Valeo AC Indonesia', 'pt-valeo-ac-indonesia', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/65408/images/logo/65408_logo_0_852625.jpg', '', 'Batam (Kepulauan Riau) - Mukakuning', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lain', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '200 - 500 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed>Dengan berkembang pesatnya dunia bisnis, kami mengundang individu - individu yang berkualitas untuk dapat bergabung dan maju bersama perusahaan kami.</div><div xss=removed>We offer challenging career development and  good working environment, that enhance our professionals to keep growing.</div></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Kami menawarkan peluang kerja dan kesempatan berkarir yang sama untuk semua level jabatan, suasana kerja yang kondusif dan transparan, serta target kerja yang membuat Anda bisa memberikan kemampuan maksimal bagi perkembangan perusahaan. Kami juga memberikan kesempatan bagi setiap karyawan untuk meningkatkan kapasitas pribadinya sehingga mampu menjadi pengelola dan pemilik dari sebuah unit usaha secara mandiri.</div><p></p>'),
(106, 4, 'Sari Rasa Group', 'sari-rasa-group', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/25284/images/logo/25284_logo_0_293277.jpg', 'http://sarirasa.co.id/', 'Jakarta Raya', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Depend on position (Head Office / Operation)', '2000 - 5000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>Founded in 1974, the Sate Khas Senayan has always been committed to advancing traditional taste of Indonesia and cultural preservation. While collecting traditional recipes we refresh the recipe according to your taste in the present era. We continue to study the science of cooking and the art technology services. Always strive to provide original innovation, in presenting authentic Indonesian cuisine in a modern atmosphere Indonesia.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Wa are a leading Indonesian cuisine restaurant with outlets among Jabodetabek and continue to expand our business rapidly. Beside of high standard quality food, we place as highly noticed on service and customer satisfaction.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>To support our growing network of restaurants and food related business, we are always looking for bright people who embrace the service culture.</div><p></p>'),
(107, 8, 'PT Unitama Sari Mas', 'pt-unitama-sari-mas', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/20555/images/logo/20555_logo_0_473058.jpg', 'http://www.unitamasarimas.co.id/', 'Jakarta Utara (Jakarta Raya)', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Gigi, Penglihatan', 'Monday - Saturday', '200 - 500 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed><strong>Our Company</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Started in the 1980s as a trading company selling air freshener products and stationeries, we have tremendously expanded into a manufacturing and distribution company of home care products.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Today with our fully-engaged workforce, we continually seek to better serve our customers through continuous product and systems improvements, developing a lifelong learning culture and a mindset of why not and challenging the status quo.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed> </div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed><strong>Our Company</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Started in the 1980s as a trading company selling air freshener products and stationeries, we have tremendously expanded into a manufacturing and distribution company of home care products.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Today with our fully-engaged workforce, we continually seek to better serve our customers through continuous product and systems improvements, developing a lifelong learning culture and a mindset of why not and challenging the status quo.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed> </div></div><div> </div><p></p></div>'),
(108, 8, 'PT Rusli Vinilon Sakti', 'pt-rusli-vinilon-sakti', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/11909/images/logo/11909_logo_0_55133.jpg', 'http://www.vinilon.com/', 'Cileungsi (Jawa Barat)', 'Formil (Kemeja+Dasi)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><ul><li xss=removed>Dari sebuah pabrik kecil berdinding bilik di atas lahan seluas 1,5 hektar, tanggal 1 Agustus 1979, berdiri PT RUSLI VINILON SAKTI untuk turut berperan dalam pembangunan di Indonesia di sektor manufacturing pipa uPVC, PE, dan Fitting.</li><li xss=removed>Melalui kerja keras, kerjasama, dan doa, pada tahun 1990, VINILON telah mampu meningkatkan kapasitas produksi menjadi 9.000 ton per tahun dan sukses memproduksi pipa PE dengan kapasitas produksi 2000 ton per tahun.</li><li xss=removed>Guna terus mendukung proses pembangunan, pada tahun 1993, VINILON melakukan modernisasi dan memindahkan pabrik yang berdiri di atas lahan seluas 13,4 Ha di Jl. Narogong, Cileungsi - Bogor. Kapasitas produksi Vinilon meningkat menjadi 18 ribu ton per tahun.</li><li xss=removed>Pada tahun-tahun berikutnya dan hingga saat ini, VINILON terus melakukan peningkatan kapasitas produksi, kualitas produk dan berbagai inovasi guna menghasilkan produk terbaik.</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>VINILON </strong>adalah pilihan utama untuk sistem Pipa uPVC/PE berkualitas. Karenanya apabila Anda membeli atau menggunakan pipa VINILON, Anda akan mendapatkan jauh lebih lengkap daripada hanya sekedar pipa. Pipa uPVC/PE berkualitas merupakan hasil produksi PT. RUSLI VINILON SAKTI Jakarta sejak tahun 1979, didukung oleh tenaga terdidik dan terlatih dibidang Pipa uPVC/PE serta kelengkapan fasilitas pengendalian mutu, teknis produksi sepenuhnya dari teknologi Jerman, maka kami menjamin bentuk dan kualitas hasil produksi selalu konsisten dan handal</div><div xss=removed> </div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>5 Prinsip Utama Bekerja di Vinilon:</div><ul><li xss=removed>Utamakan tanggung jawab dan akuntabilitas</li><li xss=removed>Utamakan menyesuaikan diri dengan kemajuan zaman</li><li xss=removed>Utamakan berjuang untuk perbaikan</li><li xss=removed>Utamakan kerja saman</li><li xss=removed>Utamakan berlaku jujur dan adil</li></ul><div xss=removed> </div><div><div xss=removed><strong>PRODUK PIPA TERLENGKAP & AKSESORISNYA</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>VINILON, produsen pipa dengan jenis produk terlengkap di Indonesia. Pipa dan aksesoris pipa VINILON menjadi solusi tepat semua kebutuhan pipa karena dapat digunakan untuk semua aplikasi, baik itu untuk air dingin dan air panas (khusus untuk waterheater), gas, serta telekomunikasi. Inovasi baru terus</div><div xss=removed>dilakukan guna menjawab tuntutan pasar yang terus berkembang.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div><div xss=removed><strong>TEKNOLOGI TERDEPAN</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>Penerapan teknologi mutakhir dari Jerman dan pengendalian mutu yang sangat ketat membuat pipa uPVC, PE, dan fitting VINILON menjadi produk pipa dan aksesoris pipa berkualitas terbaik di Indonesia</div><div xss=removed>VINILON adalah merk pipa uPVC (Unplasticizer Polyvinyl Chloride) dan pipa PE (Polyethylene), serta peralatan bantunya (accessories) ber-standard International, hasil produksi berteknologi mutakhir dari Jerman.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div><div xss=removed><strong>VARIAN PRODUK YANG LENGKAP</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>VINILON adalah pabrikan pipa berkapasitas produksi terbesar dengan jenis produk terlengkap di Indonesia</div><div xss=removed>Kapasitas produksi besar menjadikan VINILON selalu mampu memenuhi kebutuhan pasar. Tersedia berbagai jenis dan ukuran pipa serta aksesoris pipa yang memudahkan konsumen mendapatkan pipa berkualitas terbaik sesuai kebutuhan.</div></div></div></div><div xss=removed> </div><div><div xss=removed><strong>RAMAH LINGKUNGAN</strong></div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>VINILON memiliki komitmen tinggi dalam menjaga kelestarian alam</div><ul><li xss=removed>Semua produk VINILON adalah produk ramah lingkungan yang bisa di daur ulang dan tidak menghasilkan limbah dalam proses produksinya</li><li xss=removed>Penggunaan tenaga listrik dari gas dalam proses produksi mampu menekan kadar emisi CO2 dan lebih ramah lingkungan</li><li xss=removed>VINILON menerapkan sistem pipa berkonsep efisien & anti bocor sehingga mampu menghemat sumber daya air</li><li xss=removed>Aktifitas dalam mendukung anti global warming selalu diterapkan</li></ul></div><div> </div><p></p>'),
(109, 3, 'PT Infinitium Solutions', 'pt-infinitium-solutions', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/24703/images/logo/24703_logo_0_552485.jpg', 'http://www.infinitium.com/', 'Jakarta Pusat (Jakarta Raya)', 'Formil (Kemeja+Dasi)', 'Indonesia & Inggris', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>PT Infinitium Solutions, a member of the Infinitium Group of companies provides end to- end solution to our customers venturing into the world of e-Business. From Web based applications, E-payment services to Mobile services, we have complete and comprehensive solutions to cater to our clients unique business environment needs. Over the years, the success of our business has been proven with reputable clients from various State Government, large MNCs, large Enterprises and SMIs. We are seeking committed and result-oriented team players for the following positions to be part of the dynamic team in Jakarta Office.</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Infinitium offers a richly rewarding career to build people and next­generation solutions in online payment programmes. We work among friends where you benefit from the face time with senior management and unhindered access to the group CEO.</div><div>Your key performance indicators are set concurrently with your manager where the goals and how they are measured are mutually agreed. Goals will be challenging and fulfilling so that you can grow.</div><p></p>');
