(110, 12, 'PT Paradise Perkasa', 'pt-paradise-perkasa', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/504/images/logo/504_logo_0_7490985.jpg', 'http://www.paradiseperkasa.com/', 'Tangerang (Banten) - Dadap', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Tunjangan lain', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>We are Oil, Gas, Petrochemical & Industrial Supply Company, which holding ISO 9001 Certificated.</div><div>PT. PARADISE PERKASA was established in 1993 during a period of rapid expansion in the petrochemical and oil & gas industries. We are now considered by many to have one of the largest and most extensive stock selections for piping system in Indonesia. <div>We emphasize the supply of high quality materials mainly to engineering fabricators, contractors, petrochemical industries, power station, oil refineries oil & gas Industries.</div> Our policy is to provide the most comprehensive and reliable service in the metal industries as we realize that it is what most of our customers demand. Therefore, we ensure that our personnel keep in touch with our clients through computer-aided system and maintain all key client information and stocks data in order to provide our clients with a high standard of service. As proven by our recent ISO 9001:2015 Quality Standard award, which was obtained in 2002.</div><div> </div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Our Vision <div><br> To be a global integrated piping stockist with quality products and excellence service, which provide a value added to our customers.<br><br> Our Mission</div><br> To distribute high quality products that well known globally recognized in order to provide the excellence performance standard to our customer. <div> </div><div>Our Culture</div><br> 1. Commitment <div>    I commit 100% to company\'s Vision and Mission</div><div> </div> 2. Honesty <div>    I always speak and act honest to company</div><div> </div> 3. Team Work <div>     Team is \"Together Everyone Achieve More\". I always work proactively as a team and cooperate with other  team members to achieve the best result in any circumtances</div><div> </div> 4. Improvement <div>    I always improve my thoughts, energy, attention based on today is better than yesterday and tomorrow is better than today mind set. Always continually learn all of positive things and also learn from mistakes in order to achieve an excellence improvement</div><div> </div> 5. Excellence <div>    I always deliver products and services of exceptional quality that add value to all involved for the long term.   I look for ways to do more with less and stay on a path of constant and never ending improvement and innovation.</div></div><div> </div><p></p>'),
(111, 30, 'PT Gemala Kempa Daya', 'pt-gemala-kempa-daya', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/18520/images/logo/18520_logo_0_542196.jpg', '', 'Jakarta Utara (Jakarta Raya), Karawang (Jawa Barat)', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '500 - 1000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT Gemala Kempa Daya is a domestic investment company as a subsidiary of PT. Astra International Tbk producing Frame Chassis and Press Parts. Occupied an area of 45,353m2 in Pegangsaan - Jakarta and 54,030m2 in Cikampek - West Java.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div><div xss=removed>PT Gemala Kempa Daya has been certified ISO / TS 16949 as one of the company\'s commitment in making quality products in accordance with the international standard automotive quality management system through the bussines activities of the company\'s effective and efficient process. In its implementation, PT. Gemala Kempa Daya is always striving and consistent to achieve customer satisfaction with standardization of products and processes to ensure the products produced always in accordance with established standards.</div></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div xss=removed><strong>Our Vision</strong>            :</div><div xss=removed>To be world class automotive frame chassis manufacturer with excellent engineering competence.</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Our Mission</strong>        :</div><div xss=removed>To provide unique and innovative process solution that deliver best quality and value to our customers.</div><div xss=removed>To provide best value to our stakeholders</div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed><strong>Our Core Value</strong> :</div><div xss=removed>To maintain passion for excellence, team work, trustworthy & reliable and customer focus.</div><div xss=removed> </div></div><p></p>'),
(112, 14, 'PT BCA Finance', 'pt-bca-finance', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/61/images/logo/61_logo_0_7016513.jpg', 'http://bcafinance.co.id/', 'Bogor (Jawa Barat)', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia', 'Kesehatan, Pinjaman, Gigi', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1000 - 2000 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><b>PT.  BCA Finance, a fast-growing automotive financing company of BCA Group and one of the main leader in financing industries in Indonesia, is looking for young professionals to fill in the following position</b></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div> VISI</div><div><br> \"Menjadi Perusahaan terkemuka dalam industri pembiayaan di Indonesia yang memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada para stakeholders\"<br><br> Perusahaan Terkemuka</div><div><br> Terkemuka” berarti menjadi yang terdepan dalam memberikan nilai yang unggul dan berkelanjutan dalam jangka panjang kepada para stakeholders, sebagaimana dijabarkan dalam pernyataan misi kami.<br><br> ·      Industri Pembiayaan di Indonesia<br> BCA Finance memfokuskan diri pada industri mulfinance, sekalipun portofolio pembiayaan saat ini didominasi oleh pembiayaan untuk mobil. BCA Finance akan mendiversifikasi produk-produknya untuk mempertahankan tingkat perrtumbuhannya.<br><br> ·      Memberikan NILAI TERBAIK Kepada Para Stakeholders<br> Kalimat ini didefinisikan lebih lanjut dalam pernyataan misi kami.<br><br><br> MISI</div><div><br> ·       Kami memberikan NILAI TERBAIK untuk memuaskan para pelanggan sebagai pilihan utama mereka dengan memberikan produk dan jasa yang berkualitas tinggi, inovatif, dan handal.<br><br> ·       Kami memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada para rekan distribusi dengan mengembangkan hubungan saling percaya dan partnership menang-menang yang terfokus pada pertumbuhan yang berkesinambungan.</div><div><br> ·       Kami memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada para pemegang saham dan kreditur dengan menciptakan pertumbuhan keuangan dan tingkat pengembalian yang dapat dipertahankan dalam jangka panjang dengan tingkat risiko yang dapat diterima.</div><div><br> ·      Kami memahami tanggung jawab sosial kami sebagai korporat dan memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada masyarakat dengan secara aktif berkontribusi terhadap kesejahteraan mereka.</div><div><br> ·       Kami yakin bahwa hasil-hasil yang dapat dipertahankan dalam jangka panjang untuk para stakeholders hanya dapat dicapai dengan memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada orang-orang kami dengan merekrut, mengembangkan dan memberikan imbalan kepada orang-orang yang berkompetensi tinggi dan menciptakan iklim kerja yang kondusif di mana orang-orang dapat bertumbuh dan berinovasi.</div><div><br> ·       Kami memberikan NILAI TERBAIK kepada para supplier dengan memperlakukan mereka secara fair dan prinsip \"menang-menang\".</div><p></p>'),
(113, 16, 'PT. POMI ( Paiton Operation & Maintenance Indonesia )', 'pt-pomi', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/12832/images/logo/12832_logo_0_566865.png', 'http://www.pomi.co.id/', 'Probolinggo (Jawa Timur) - Paiton', 'Bisnis (kemeja)', 'Indonesia & Inggris', 'Kesehatan, Gigi, Olahraga', 'Sabtu / Memerlukan shift', '50 - 200 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>PT. POMI is the first and the largest Independent Power Producer (IPP) operating in Indonesia. We currently have three power plant in East Java and provide 2.045 MW of power to PT. PLN (Persero), supplying power to Java, Madura and Bali, which are home to 150 million people. We are also providing job opportunities to around people. </div><div xss=removed> </div><div xss=removed>We are seeking qualified professionals employees to fill the following positions:</div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>We offer the same job opportunities and career opportunities for all levels of work, a conducive and transparent work atmosphere, and work targets that allow you to provide maximum capacity for the development of the company. We also provide opportunities for every employee to increase his personal capacity so that he is able to become the manager and owner of a business unit independently</div><p></p>'),
(114, 19, 'PT Kloverkres Solusi Integrasi', 'pt-kloverkres-solusi-integrasi', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/216416/images/logo/216416_logo_0_830551.jpg', 'http://www.kloverkres.co.id/', 'Jakarta Selatan (Jakarta Raya) - Bintaro', '', 'http://www.kloverkres.co.id/', 'Kesehatan', 'Regular, Senin - Jum;at', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div><div>PT Kloverkres Solusi Integrasi, www.kloverkres.co.id, adalah perusahaan Software Developer yang bergerak di berbagai bidang, seperti Manufacturing, Healthcare, Banking, Parking, dan payment switching, dan mempunyai klien di dalam dan luar negeri. Kami adalah outsource partner dari TekSystem dan CXC Asia.</div></div><p></p></div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div>Analyze, learn, and solve. This is our value. We make our clients\' businesses better, one byte at a time.</div><p></p>'),
(115, 24, 'PT Kasyasindo Megah Perkasa', 'pt-kasyaindo-megah-perkasa', 'https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/19991/images/logo/19991_logo_0.jpg', '', 'Bali', '', '', '', '', '1 - 50 Pekerja', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"><p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"></p><div xss=removed>KASYASINDO adalah perusahaan swasta Nasional yang bergerak dibidang Sumber Daya Manusia ( Jasa Outsourcing, Business Prosses Outsourcing, Payroll Management dan Executive Search ). Didirikan oleh para staff ahli dibidang Management Sumber Daya Manusia. Berangkat dari Oprimis yang tinggi tentang pemikiran untuk meningkatkan sumber daya manusia yang memiliki nilai produktifitas dan mampu bersaing didalam dunia kerja.</div><p></p></div>', '');
